up%20a%20'fact-checking'%20unit%20to%20monitor%20'fake%20news'%20on%20social%20media%20-%20including%20reports%20posted%20by%20media%20organisations%20-%20has%20been%20red-flagged%20by%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India.%20On%20Sunday%20the%20EGI%20issued%20a%20statement%20referring%20to%20its%20petition%20challenging%20amendments%20to%20the%20IT%20Rules%20(2023)%20in%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20and%20warned%20against%20a%20%26quot%3Bfact-checking%20unit...%20under%20the%20executive%20(with)%20sole%20authority%20to%20determine%20what%20is%20fake%20or%20not%2C%20and%20powers%20to%20order%20content%20take-down%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EGI%20admitted%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20a%20problem%20of%20misinformation%20and%20fake%20news%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20online%20space%26quot%3B%20but%20said%20efforts%20to%20identify%20and%20remove%20such%20content%20had%20to%20be%20led%20by%20%26quot%3Bindependent%20bodies%20that%20are%20not%20under%20the%20sole%20purview%20of%20the%20government%2C%20lest%20they%20become%20tools%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20voices%20of%20dissent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20monitoring%20framework%20should%20follow%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice%2C%20including%20journalists%20and%20media%20bodies%2C%20so%20that%20press%20freedom%20is%20not%20tampered%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EGI%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Guild%20urges%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20to%20clearly%20specify%20the%20scope%20of%20and%20powers%20of%20the%20proposed%20fact-checking%20unit%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20governing%20mechanism%20under%20which%20it%20will%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EGI%20added%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bconsultation%20exercise%20with%20press%20organisations%26quot%3B%20to%20develop%20this%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEGI%20notes%20with%20concern%2C%20some%20aspects%20of%2