ompared%20to%2015%20in%202022.%20December%202022%20was%20the%20deadliest%20month%2C%20with%20three%20suicides%20in%20a%20single%20day.%20Data%20shows%20that%20the%20number%20of%20suicides%20has%20increased%20by%2060%25%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20However%2C%20that%20jump%20in%20deaths%20is%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20number%20of%20students%20in%20Kota%20declined%20in%202019%20and%202020%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%2010%20students%20ended%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20city%20compared%20to%2012%20in%202018%20and%20nine%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Dr%20Bharat%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20head%20of%20the%20psychiatry%20department%20at%20Kota%20Medical%20College%2C%20said%20that%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20comprehensive%20change%20in%20the%20approach%20of%20both%20the%20coaching%20institutes%20and%20the%20parents%20to%20curb%20the%20alarming%20rate%20of%20student%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20suicides%20by%20students%20in%20Kota%20is%20the%20highest%20this%20year.%20We%20have%20been%20presenting%20suggestions%20to%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20for%2020%20years%2C%20but%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Shekhawat%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%2C%20there%20was%20no%20pressure%20on%20students%20as%20they%20had%20the%20support%20of%20their%20families%20and%20were%20at%20home.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20lockdown%2C%20the%20pressure%20has%20returned%2C%20and%20that%20umbrella%20support%20has%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudents%20who%20are%20admitted%20to%20coaching%20institutes%20at%20the%20age%20of%2015%20or%2016%20are%20too%20young.%20They%20miss%20out%20on%20the%20benefits%20of%20school%2C%20such%20as%20extracurricular%20activities%20and%20friendships.%20They%20are%20also%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20stress%20due%20to%20the%20rigorous%20coaching%20schedule.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shekhawat%20suggested%20a%20minimum%20age%20for%20admission%20at%20Kota's%20coaching%20institutes%20so%20that%20the%20students%20are%20not%20thrown%20into%20the%20rigours%20of%20academia%20before%20they%20have%20matured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCoaching%20institutes%20should%20also%20regulate%20the%20coaching%20industry%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20institutes%20provide%20a%20healthy%20and%20supportive%20environment%20for%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20over%202%20lakh%20students%20move%20to%20Kota%20to%20prepare%20for%20competitive%20exams%20such%20as%20the%20JEE%20and%20NEET.%20Following%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20student%20suicides%2C%20authorities%20have%20asked%20coaching%20institutes%20to%20suspend%20routine%20tests%20for%20the%20next%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20combat%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20suicides%2C%20spring-loaded%20fans%20were%20installed%20in%20all%20hostels%20and%20paying%20guest%20(PG)%20accommodations%20in%20Kota.%20%26quot%3BAnti-suicide%20nets%26quot%3B%20are%20also%20being%20installed%20in%20balconies%20and%20lobbies%20of%20hostels%20so%20that%20students%20cannot%20jump%20to%20their%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHostel%20owners%20have%20said%20that%20the%20exercise%20to%20install%20nets%20and%20spring-loaded%20fans%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20making%20their%20premises%20%26quot%3Bsuicide-proof%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20installed%20huge%20nets%20in%20all%20lobbies%20and%20balconies%20to%20block%20students%20in%20case%20they%20jump%20from%20higher%20floors.%20These%20nets%20can%20hold%20weight%20up%20to%20150%20kg%20and%20also%20ensure%20that%20students%20do%20not%20get%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20hostel%20owner%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20also%20passed%20directions%20to%20provide%20mental%20health%20support%20to%20st