20supply%20chain%20concerns%20caused%20by%20health%20crises%2C%20disasters%2C%20and%20geopolitical%20events.%20The%20coronavirus%20crisis%20and%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20are%20among%20the%20recent%20events%20that%20disrupted%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%2C%20resulting%20in%20steep%20price%20rises%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20juncture%2C%20India%20is%20charting%20its%20way%20to%20be%20more%20involved%20in%20the%20global%20supply%20chains%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20China%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20supply%20chain%20refers%20to%20every%20step%20involved%20in%20delivering%20a%20finished%20product%20or%20service%20to%20customers.%20A%20disruption%20at%20any%20level%20leads%20to%20delays%2C%20unavailability%20or%20even%20rise%20in%20prices%2C%20affecting%20the%20markets%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20is%20the%20solution%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20trustworthy%20nation%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20highlighted%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Sunday%2C%20questioning%20the%20efficiency%20of%20the%20global%20supply%20chain%20that%20ceased%20to%20exist%20when%20the%20world%20required%20it%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20which%20has%20been%20an%20ideal%20market%20for%20the%20global%20sellers%2C%20is%20now%20emerging%20as%20a%20manufacturing%20hub%20with%20an%20immense%20potential.%20Several%20top%20companies%20like%20Apple%20have%20already%20started%20production%20in%20India%20while%20the%20country%20aims%20to%20begin%20domestic%20microchips%20production%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demand%20for%20Indian%20goods%20has%20increased%20at%20the%20global%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20citing%20his%20'Vocal%20for%20Local'%20mantra%20that%20seeks%20to%20boost%20domestic%20production%20in%20a%20more%20globalized%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20supply%20chain%20resilience%20and%20sustainability%20must%20now%20be%20the%20focus%20to%20take%20businesses%20beyond%20the%20bottomline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20too%20asserted%20that%20India%20is%20eyeing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20supply%20chain%20through%20its%20output-incentive%20plans%20and%20the%20growth%20of%20its%20domestic%20consumer%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20production-linked%20incentive%20schemes%20are%20bringing%20global%20value%20chains%20to%20India%20which%20will%20help%20the%20country%20become%20a%20bulk%20producer%20of%20manufactured%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20also%20eyeing%20a%20key%20space%20in%20the%20electronics%20sector%20with%20'Made%20in%20India'%20laptops%20and%20computers.%20It%20has%20already%20become%20the%20second%20largest%20producer%20of%20mobile%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20western%20world%20is%20shifting%20its%20supply%20chains%20from%20China%20in%20view%20of%20the%20geopolitical%20situation%20and%20India%20seeks%20to%20make%20most%20of%20this%20opportunity.%20The%20government%20has%20set%20an%20ambitious%20target%20of%20reaching%20%242%20trillion%20in%20overall%20exports%20every%20year%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693203900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-02%2Fk6e2tg28_trade-generic-pixabay-650_650x400_16_February_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-india-eyes-key-role-in-global-supply-chains-4335301%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20is%20eyeing%20solutions%20to%20its%20supply%20chain%20concerns%20caused%20by%20health%20crises%2C%20disasters%2C%20and%20geopolitical%20events.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-india-eyes-key-role-in-global-supply-chains-4335301%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-india-eyes-key-role-in-global-supply-chains-4335301%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-india-eyes-key-role-in-global-supply-chains-4335301%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Govt%20to%20Transport%20Essentials%20to%20Churachandpur%20Through%20Aerial%20Routes%2C%20With%20Army%20Help%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15203438%2FSurgical-ward-at-Churachandpur-hospital-II.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Manipur%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20coordinate%20with%20the%20Indian%20army%20and%20other%20central%20security%20forces%20to%20start%20transporting%20essential%20commodities%20to%20the%20hill%20district%20of%20Churachandpur%20from%20August%2028%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-tribal-district-to-get-essentials-via-alternative-routes%2Farticle67241952.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Manipur%20government%20official%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20it%20is%20ensuring%20that%20medical%20supplies%20reach%20the%20district%20through%20aerial%20routes%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%2C%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Manipur%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20measures%20have%20been%20taken%20because%20the%20government%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20open%20the%20land%20routes%20within%20the%20strife-torn%20state.%20Ethnic%20violence%20has%20roiled%20Manipur%20since%20May%203%2C%20killing%20upwards%20of%20150%20people%20and%20displacing%20tens%20of%20thousands.%20The%20state%20is%20now%20divided%20into%20territories%20controlled%20by%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20blockades%20are%20on%20at%20the%20National%20Highway%20that%20connects%20Dimapur%20and%20Imphal%2C%20and%20on%20the%20Churachandpur%20Road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20began%20on%20August%2021%2C%20and%20was%20called%20by%20the%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20(COTU)%20at%20Kangpokpi.%20This%20has%20affected%20the%20supply%20of%20essentials%20to%20Meitei%20dominated%20places.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20critical%20situation%20as%20an%20alternative%20route%20exists%20to%20supply%20the%20valley%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20Churachandpur%20is%20blocked%20by%20women-led%20Meitei%20groups%20and%20transporters%20have%20refused%20to%20ply%20on%20their%20routes%20citing%20personal%20safety%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20so%20far%20also%20failed%20to%20give%20access%20to%20the%20airport%20at%20Imphal%20to%20the%20hill%20residents%2C%20particularly%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community.%20Those%20located%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20have%20to%20wheel%20down%20to%20neighbouring%20Nagaland%20to%20board%20a%20flight%20from%20Dimapur%20airport.%20The%20Kukis%20from%20the%20Churachandpur%20area%20have%20been%20taking%20the%20day-long%20road%20route%20to%20Aizawl%20in%20Mizoram%20for%20air%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthree-months-later-has-amit-shah-fulfilled-the-promises-he-made-on-manipur%5C%22%3Ereported%20earlier%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20helicopter%20service%20to%20the%20Imphal%20airport%20from%20the%20hill%20areas%20has%20not%20taken%20off%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20in%20depth%20how%20one%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20promises%20to%20Manipur%2C%20during%20his%20visit%2C%20was%20that%20eight%20medical%20teams%20would%20be%20sent%20there.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20teams%20will%20provide%20health%20facilities%20in%20Moreh%2C%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20found%20that%2035%20people%20have%20already%20died%20in%20Churachandpur%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20medicines%20and%20proper%20treatment%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20the%20district%2C%20according%20to%20Kuki%20Khanglai%20Lawmpi%2C%20a%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20organisation%20that%20has%20been%20providing%20medical%20aid%20in%20relief%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publishing%20the%20report%2C%20there%20is%20a%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20in%20Saparmeina%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%2C%20and%20that%20six%20people%20are%20in%20immediate%20need%20of%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%20has%20been%20raised%20by%20the%20Kuki%20community%20due%20to%20the%20May%203%20violence%2C%20powerful%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20organisations%20like%20COCOMI%20have%20been%20holding%20rallies%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%20with%20the%20counter%20demand%20that%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20Manipur%20must%20be%20maintained.%20However%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20latest%20measures%20to%20reach%20one%20large%20part%20of%20the%20state%20aerially%20only%20indicates%20its%20inability%20to%20surmount%20the%20territorial%20divide%20created%20post%20May%203%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693203165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15203438%2FSurgical-ward-at-Churachandpur-hospital-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchurachandpur-blockade-air-route-essential-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20measures%20have%20been%20taken%20because%20the%20government%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20open%20the%20land%20routes%20within%20the%20strife-torn%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamir%20hosts%20a%20get-together%20for%20LSC%20team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693203064000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103124094%2Cimgsize-48294.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faamir-khan-hosts-a-get-together-for-team-laal-singh-chaddha-report%2Farticleshow%2F103124094.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103124094.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAamir%20Khan%20reportedly%20hosted%20a%20get-together%20party%20for%20the%20team%20of%20'Laal%20Singh%20Chaddha'%20to%20celebrate%20the%20film's%20success%20on%20OTT%20platforms.%20Naga%20Chaitanya%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20film%2C%20praised%20Aamir's%20work%20ethic%20and%20said%20he%20sees%20working%20on%20the%20project%20as%20an%20investment%20for%20the%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20'The%20Shawshank%20Redemption'%20And%20India's%20Criminal%20Justice%20System%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BThe%20Shawshank%20Redemption%2C%26quot%3B%20Andy%20Dufresne%2C%20a%20banker%20wrongfully%20accused%20of%20murdering%20his%20wife%2C%20endures%20two%20decades%20at%20Shawshank%20Prison.%20While%20incarcerated%2C%20he%20uses%20his%20banking%20skills%20to%20assist%20the%20corrupt%20warden%20in%20money%20laundering.%20The%20movie%20isn't%20just%20about%20Andy's%20eventual%20escape%20but%20also%20systemic%20corruption%2C%20misuse%20of%20power%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20reform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20criminal%20justice%20system%2C%20rooted%20in%20colonial-era%20laws%2C%20can%20be%20likened%20to%20the%20imposing%20walls%20of%20Shawshank.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20the%20visible%20bricks%20and%20mortar%20(the%20dated%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%2C%20the%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%20and%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Act%2C%201898)%20but%20the%20structures%20of%20power%20and%20control%20that%20have%20been%20perpetuated%20over%20the%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%2C%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20(BS)%20Bill%2C%20and%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20(BNSS)%2C%20introduced%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20signify%20much-needed%20renovation.%20However%2C%20as%20Foucault%20would%20suggest%2C%20this%20overhaul%20isn't%20just%20about%20replacing%20outdated%20statutes.%20It's%20about%20reassessing%20the%20foundations%20of%20justice%2C%20power%20structures%2C%20and%20societal%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20colonial%20legacy%20is%20a%20critical%20component%20of%20this%20reform%2C%20it%20doesn't%20stand%20alone.%20A%20modern%20and%20effective%20criminal%20justice%20system%20must%20be%20sensitive%20to%20gender%20justice%2C%20understanding%20that%20crimes%20against%20women%20are%20not%20just%20individual%20acts%20but%20are%20reflective%20of%20deeply%20entrenched%20societal%20power%20dynamics.%20The%20new%20reforms%20promise%20more%20stringent%20punishment%20for%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20system%20is%20not%20just%20punitive%2C%20but%20also%20protective.%20In%20this%20column%2C%20we%20discuss%20five%20big%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(1)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%C2%A0The%20definitions%20of%20rape%20in%20IPC%20Section%20375%20and%20BNS%20Section%2063%20differ%20significantly%2C%20with%20BNS%20being%20more%20comprehensive.%20While%20IPC%20emphasizes%20penetration%20as%20the%20act%20of%20rape%2C%20BNS%20broadens%20the%20scope%20to%20include%20various%20other%20acts%2C%20such%20as%20insertion%20of%20objects%20or%20manipulation%20to%20cause%20penetration.%20BNS%20also%20extends%20the%20circumstances%20that%20negate%20consent%2C%20covers%20a%20wider%20age%20range%20(up%20to%2018)%2C%20and%20adds%20specific%20exceptions%20to%20medical%20procedures.%20Overall%2C%20BNS's%20definition%20is%20more%20aligned%20with%20a%20modern%20understanding%20of%20consent%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%20making%20it%20a%20more%20encompassing%20approach%20to%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(2)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%C2%A0The%20distinction%20between%20the%20punishments%20for%20rape%20under%20the%20BNS%20and%20the%20IPC%20highlight%20different%20approaches%20and%20considerations.%20The%20BNS%20appears%20to%20have%20specific%20categorizations%20for%20punishment%2C%20factoring%20in%20victim's%20age%2C%20circumstances%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20relationship%20to%20the%20victim%2C%20and%20additional%20scenarios%20such%20as%20deceitful%20means%20or%20acting%20in%20a%20group.%20The%20punishment%20under%20BNS%20tend%20to%20have%20higher%20minimum%20sentences%2C%20with%20provisions%20for%20both%20imprisonment%20and%20fines%2C%20extending%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20or%20even%20the%20death%20penalty%20in%20extreme%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IPC%20outlines%20a%20more%20generalised%20approach%20to%20rape%20punishment%2C%20with%20a%20minimum%20jail%20term%20of%20seven%20years%2C%20extending%20up%20to%20life%20imprisonment%2C%20along%20with%20fines.%20There%20are%20provisions%20for%20less%20severe%20penalties%20with%20special%20reasoning%2C%20and%20specific%20clauses%20related%20to%20official%20positions%2C%20such%20as%20police%20officers%20and%20public%20servants.%20Overall%2C%20the%20BNS%20seems%20more%20nuanced%20and%20stringent%20in%20its%20approach%20to%20rape%20punishment%2C%20reflecting%20more%20detailed%20consideration%20of%20different%20contexts%20and%20circumstances%2C%20while%20the%20IPC%20provides%20a%20broader%20framework%20with%20some%20flexibility%20for%20judicial%20discretion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(3)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%C2%A0One%20of%20the%20positive%20aspects%20of%20BNS%20is%20that%20it%20doesn't%20fixate%20on%20a%20specific%20value%20for%20fines.%20In%20India%2C%20fines%20typically%20remain%20low%2C%20as%20they%20are%20determined%20by%20legislation.%20Consequently%2C%20to%20alter%20these%20fines%2C%20it's%20necessary%20to%20pass%20an%20amendment%20through%20parliament.%20In%20contrast%2C%20BNS%20provides%20a%20more%20flexible%20approach%20by%20stipulating%20that%20fines%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bjust%20and%20reasonable%26quot%3B%20to%20cover%20the%20victim's%20medical%20costs%20and%20rehabilitation.%20This%20approach%20centers%20on%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20ensuring%20her%20financial%20stability%20and%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(4)%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20provisions%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20the%20BNS%20regarding%20assault%20and%20criminal%20force%20against%20women%20underline%20society's%20efforts%20to%20protect%20women%20from%20various%20forms%20of%20harassment%20and%20assault.%20Section%20354%20of%20the%20IPC%20focuses%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bintention%20to%20outrage%20the%20modesty%20of%20a%20woman%26quot%3B%20through%20assault%20or%20criminal%20force%2C%20punishable%20by%20up%20to%20two%20years'%20imprisonment.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20BNS%20provides%20a%20more%20detailed%2C%20comprehensive%2C%20and%20harsher%20set%20of%20punishments%20for%20similar%20offenses.%20Section%2073%20echoes%20IPC's%20Section%20354%20but%20mandates%20a%20minimum%20imprisonment%20of%20one%20year%2C%20which%20can%20extend%20to%20five.%20Also%2C%20the%20BNS%20has%20also%20clubbed%20all%20the%20given%20offences%20under%20the%20subheading%20%26quot%3BOf%20criminal%20force%20and%20assault%20against%20women%26quot%3B%20sexual%20harassment%20(Section%2074)%2C%20intent%20to%20disrobe%20(Section%2075)%2C%20voyeurism%20(Section%2076)%2C%20and%20stalking%20(Section%2077)%2C%20each%20with%20its%20specific%20definitions%20and%20corresponding%20punishment%20and%20penalties.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20BNS%20aims%20for%20a%20more%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20offenses%20against%20women%20and%20envisions%20stricter%20consequences%20for%20offenders.%20By%20specifying%20various%20forms%20of%20harassment%20and%20assault%2C%20the%20BNS%20is%20more%20expansive%20in%20its%20protective%20approach%2C%20emphasizing%20not%20just%20the%20physical%2C%20but%20also%20the%20emotional%20and%20psychological%20harm%20such%20acts%20can%20inflict%20on%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(5)%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0In%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20gender-neutral%20offenses%20is%20paramount%20for%20ensuring%20fairness%2C%20equality%2C%20and%20modernity.%20Traditional%20gender-based%20definitions%20of%20crimes%20can%20lead%20to%20biases%20and%20inequalities%2C%20reinforcing%20stereotypes%20that%20don't%20align%20with%20the%20diverse%20and%20complex%20realities%20of%20human%20behavior.%20Gender%20neutrality%20in%20the%20law%20acknowledges%20that%20an%20offense%20can%20be%20committed%20by%20anyone%2C%20regardless%20of%20gender%2C%20and%20promotes%20a%20more%20inclusive%20and%20just%20legal%20framework.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20the%20BNS's%20move%20to%20make%20various%20offenses%20gender-neutral%20is%20a%20commendable%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20It%20not%20only%20reflects%20a%20more%20evolved%20and%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20criminal%20behavior%20but%20also%20symbolizes%20a%20shift%20towards%20a%20more%20gender-inclusive%20and%20modern%20criminal%20justice%20system.%20Such%20progressive%20changes%20underscore%20the%20commitment%20to%20equality%20and%20non-discrimination%2C%20essential%20principles%20for%20a%20fair%20and%20just%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20shift%20from%20the%20archaic%20provisions%20of%20the%20IPC%20to%20the%20more%20contemporary%20and%20nuanced%20stipulations%20of%20the%20BNS%20is%20akin%20to%20breaking%20free%20from%20the%20oppressive%20walls%20of%20Shawshank.%20By%20focusing%20on%20a%20detailed%20and%20victim-centric%20approach%20to%20gender%20justice%2C%20the%20BNS%20not%20only%20fortifies%20legal%20safeguards%20but%20also%20begins%20to%20reshape%20societal%20understanding.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20lays%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20legal%20system%20where%20gender%20equality%20is%20not%20merely%20an%20aspirational%20goal%20but%20an%20attainable%20reality%2C%20marking%20an%20essential%20stride%20towards%20a%20just%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20modern%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBibek%20Debroy%20is%20the%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20(EAC-PM)%20%26amp%3B%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20Additional%20Private%20Secretary%20(Policy%20%26amp%3B%20Research)%2C%20EAC-PM.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20authors.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693202940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fatt9hsso_court-generic_625x300_27_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fof-legal-reforms-gender-justice-and-indias-shawshank-redemption-4335219%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BThe%20Shawshank%20Redemption%2C%26quot%3B%20Andy%20Dufresne%2C%20a%20banker%20wrongfully%20accused%20of%20murdering%20his%20wife%2C%20endures%20two%20decades%20at%20Shawshank%20Prison.%20While%20incarcerated%2C%20he%20uses%20his%20banking%20skills%20to%20assist%20the%20corrupt%20warden%20in%20money%20laundering.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fof-legal-reforms-gender-justice-and-indias-shawshank-redemption-4335219%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fof-legal-reforms-gender-justice-and-indias-shawshank-redemption-4335219%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fof-legal-reforms-gender-justice-and-indias-shawshank-redemption-4335219%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anger%20Brews%20in%20Jammu%20as%20Traders%2C%20Locals%20Accuse%20the%20BJP%20of%20Misgovernance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120115%2FJammu-bandh-pic-01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CKashmiris%20were%20100%25%20better%20than%20you%20(Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party).%20We%20were%20happy%20with%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20they%20are%20destroying%20us.%20Article%20370%20was%20our%20identity%20and%20safety.%20We%20are%20Dogras!%20Kashmiris%20were%20also%20scared%20of%20us.%20We%20would%20boast%20of%20our%20Dogra%20identity.%20If%20they%20(Kashmiri%20politicians)%20would%20get%20Rs%2020%2C%20they%20would%20give%20us%20Rs%2010.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20utterances%20of%20the%20father%20of%20the%20president%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Yuva%20Rajput%20Sabha%2C%20an%20organisation%20spearheading%20protests%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20to%20seek%20suspension%20of%20a%20toll%20plaza%20in%20Sarore%20Samba%2C%20shows%20how%20the%20thinking%20of%20people%20in%20Jammu%20has%20changed%20over%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government.%20The%20video%20in%20which%20he%20makes%20these%20remarks%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20over%20the%20toll%20plaza%20have%20become%20a%20platform%20for%20Jammuities%20to%20vent%20their%20anger%20over%20a%20series%20of%20moves%20by%20the%20union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20unelected%20government%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20reorganisation%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20August%202019.%20The%20region%20observed%20a%20complete%20shutdown%20on%20August%2026%20(Saturday)%20and%20witnessed%20protests%20and%20slogans%20against%20the%20union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20administration%20and%20the%20BJP.%20The%20protests%20in%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20citadel%20over%20governance%20issues%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20LG-led%20administration%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20on%20the%20path%20of%20progress%20and%20development%20after%20the%20constitutional%20changes%20of%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20the%20protests%20begin%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20with%20the%20Yuva%20Rajput%20Sabha%20(YRS)%20issuing%20an%20ultimatum%20to%20the%20administration%20to%20suspend%20toll%20collection%20at%20Sarore%20Plaza%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20condition%20of%20the%20road%20and%20damage%20to%20a%20bridge%20at%20Dayalachak%20on%20the%20Jammu-Pathankot%20highway.%20On%20August%2021%2C%20YRS%20held%20a%20protest%20rally%20near%20the%20toll%20plaza.%20Some%20people%20also%20pelted%20stones%20at%20the%20plaza%20and%20damaged%20glass%20windows%2C%20prompting%20the%20administration%20to%20impose%20Section%20144%20around%20the%20toll%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20at%20night%20on%20August%2021%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20arrested%2026%20leaders%20from%20the%20Sarore%20toll%20post%2C%20sparking%20off%20massive%20protests%20in%20the%20region.%20Soon%2C%20opposition%20political%20parties%20joined%20in%20and%20held%20protests%20against%20the%20administration.%20On%20August%2026%2C%20the%20region%20witnessed%20a%20complete%20%3Cem%3Ebandh%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20call%20of%20the%20Jammu%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industries%20against%20the%20Sarore%20toll%20plaza%20and%20installation%20of%20smart%20electric%20metres.%20The%20protesters%20mocked%20the%20BJP%20with%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9CJammu%2C%20Jammu%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20slogan%20often%20raised%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Devinder%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120155%2FJammu-bandh-pic-06.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120155%2FJammu-bandh-pic-06.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120155%2FJammu-bandh-pic-06-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120155%2FJammu-bandh-pic-06-1024x686.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670162%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Jammu%20bandh%20on%20Saturday.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20or%20its%20earlier%20avatar%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20has%20been%20projecting%20itself%20as%20a%20protector%20of%20the%20interests%20of%20Jammu.%20The%20right-wing%20party%20has%20often%20accused%20successive%20regimes%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20of%20poor%20treatment%20towards%20the%20region%20and%20bias%20in%20favour%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%2C%20it%20had%20objected%20to%20setting%20up%20a%20toll%20plaza%20at%20Lakhanpur%20and%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20collection%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejaziya%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20Vaishno%20Devi%20pilgrims%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Katra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20workers%2C%20led%20by%20Chandra%20Prakash%20Ganga%20who%20became%20minister%20in%20the%20PDP-BJP%20coalition%20government%20in%202015%2C%20dismantled%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20Sarore%20toll%20plaza%20in%20May%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJammu%20fumes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20fourth%20time%20after%20August%205%2C%202019%20that%20Jammu%20has%20observed%20a%20shutdown%20over%20economic%20issues.%20It%20observed%20bandhs%20on%20the%20imposition%20of%20property%20tax%2C%20proposal%20of%20opening%20of%20Reliance%20retail%20stores%2C%20and%20lawyers%E2%80%99%20demand%20for%20housing%20quasi-judicial%20bodies%20and%20the%20Central%20Administrative%20Tribunal%20(CAT)%20at%20one%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJammu%20has%20been%20betrayed%20and%20backstabbed%2C%E2%80%9D%20advocate%20Sheikh%20Shakeel%20Ahmad%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Jammu%20was%20promised%20that%20its%20lands%20and%20jobs%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20compromised%2C%20but%20there%20are%20no%20safeguards%20for%20the%20region%20like%20Ladakh.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20major%20contracts%20have%20gone%20to%20outsiders.%20The%20outsiders%20have%20taken%20away%20major%20contracts%20in%20mining%20and%20others%20business%20avenues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20abolishing%20of%20the%20practice%20of%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20darbar%20move%20(moving%20the%20winter%20capital%20from%20Srinagar%20to%20Jammu)%20has%20crippled%20business%20in%20Jammu.%20%E2%80%9CLakhs%20of%20Kashmiris%20would%20visit%20Jammu%20in%20winters%20and%20spend%20crores%20of%20rupees%20here.%20Now%20less%20people%20visit%20the%20region%20after%20the%20government%20abolished%20the%20darbar%20move%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20darbar%20move%20was%20a%20149-year-old%20official%20practice%20of%20rotating%20the%20seat%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20governance%20between%20the%20twin%20capitals%20of%20Srinagar%20and%20Jammu%20on%20a%20bi-annual%20basis.%20It%20was%20abolished%20in%202021%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20led%20by%20Manoj%20Sinha%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20save%20the%20state%20exchequer%20Rs%20200%20crore%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Gupta%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Jammu%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industries%20(JCCI)%2C%20said%20that%20there%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20disturb%20the%20business%20community%20of%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20them%20(government)%20keep%20their%20focus%20on%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20don%E2%80%99t%20disturb%20us.%20We%20are%20not%20anti-nationals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120259%2FJammu-bandh-pic-04.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120259%2FJammu-bandh-pic-04.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120259%2FJammu-bandh-pic-04-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120259%2FJammu-bandh-pic-04-1024x671.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670164%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22786%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Jammu%20bandh%20on%20Saturday.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Jammu%20bandh%20was%20a%20historic%20shutdown%20and%20the%20government%20should%20talk%20to%20the%20people%20to%20understand%20their%20grievances.%20%E2%80%9CAbolition%20of%20the%20darbar%20move%20practice%20has%20not%20only%20affected%20business%20in%20the%20region%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20potential%20to%20create%20differences%20between%20two%20regions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20region%20also%20witnessed%20massive%20protests%20by%20unemployed%20youth%20in%20May%20this%20year%20over%20engagement%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblacklisted%E2%80%9D%20company%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Service%20Selection%20Board%20(SSB)%20for%20conducting%20job%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20on%20sticky%20wicket%2C%20Kashmir%20%26amp%3B%20Jammu%20come%20closer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20tight%20spot%20over%20the%20situation%20unfolding%20in%20Jammu%2C%20the%20political%20and%20psychological%20divergences%20between%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20are%20narrowing%20down%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20local%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20decisions%20of%20the%20UT%E2%80%99s%20administration.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20is%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20any%20forcible%20taxation%20or%20demolition.%20This%20tax%20(property)%20has%20not%20been%20imposed%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20the%20LG%E2%80%99s%20administration.%20However%2C%20paying%20a%20trivial%20amount%20of%20tax%20would%20ensure%20crores%20of%20funds%20for%20development%20of%20civic%20amenities%20like%20roads%2C%20electricity%2C%20lanes%2C%20water%20and%20drains%2C%E2%80%9D%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20J%26amp%3BK%20president%20Ravinder%20Raina%20told%20mediapersons%20in%20February%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Jammu%E2%80%99s%20Dogri-speaking%20areas%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20power%20tussle%20from%20Praja%20Parishad%20days%2C%20are%20becoming%20psychologically%20and%20politically%20closer%20to%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20participation%20of%20Jammu-based%20groups%20in%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20convened%20by%20National%20Conference%20president%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20over%20voting%20issue%20and%20his%20participation%20in%20the%20Panthers%20Party%20foundation%20day%20rally%20shows%20how%20leadership%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20coming%20closer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20is%20under%20direct%20central%20rule%20since%20June%202018%20when%20BJP%20withdrew%20support%20to%20Mehbooba%20Mufti-led%20government%2C%20citing%20the%20deteriorating%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20then%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20speaks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20unit%2C%20Ashok%20Koul%20said%20the%20opposition%20parties%20are%20raising%20anti-BJP%20slogans%20during%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20these%20parties%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20support%20base%20and%20are%20trying%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20LG%20Manoj%20Sinha%20had%20told%20reporters%20last%20week%20that%20he%20has%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Sarore%20toll%20plaza%20with%20the%20National%20Highway%20Authorities%20of%20India%20(NHAI).%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20NHAI%20chairman.%20This%20is%20a%20genuine%20issue.%20Local%20people%20are%20facing%20problems%20due%20to%20damage%20to%20a%20bridge.%20He%20assured%20me%20that%20they%20will%20soon%20send%20a%20team.%20I%20am%20hopeful%20that%20the%20issue%20would%20be%20resolved%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693202895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120115%2FJammu-bandh-pic-01.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanger-brews-in-jammu-as-traders-locals-accuse-the-bjp-of-misgovernance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20complete%20shutdown%20on%20Saturday%20and%20anti-BJP%20slogans%20and%20sentiments%20contradict%20the%20Union%20government's%20claims%20that%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%20has%20brought%20prosperity%20to%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20China-Japan%20seafood%20war%20could%20have%20an%20unlikely%20winner%3A%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224464%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vendors%20sort%20lobsters%20at%20a%20seafood%20and%20fish%20stall%2C%20at%20a%20seafood%20market%20in%20Beijing%2C%20China%20Aug