0and%20bodily%20strength.%20He%20had%20once%20recalled%20in%20vivid%20terms%20how%20his%20bigger%20classmates%20crushed%20his%20spirit%20through%20raw%20power%20and%20brutality.%20They%20had%20cornered%20the%20frail%20and%20young%20looking%20Mahapatra%20during%20lunch%20break.%20Dragging%20him%20against%20his%20will%2C%20they%20had%20pinned%20him%20on%20a%20desk%2C%20while%20rough%20hands%20started%20pulling%20down%20his%20shorts.%20They%20wanted%20to%20verify%20whether%20his%20body%E2%80%99s%20most%20private%20parts%20appeared%20as%20young%20as%20the%20boy%20himself%20did.%20Fifty%20years%20later%2C%20Mahapatra%20had%20written%20about%20the%20incident%20for%20an%20American%20publication.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20been%20stripped%20down%20to%20the%20wound%20of%20sex%E2%80%A6My%20body%20has%20grown%2C%20a%20snake%20curling%20about%20its%20pain%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EJayanta%20Mahapatra%20(22%20October%201928-%2027%20August%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoets%20never%20die%20as%20long%20as%20we%20read%20them%2C%20and%20Jayantada%20will%20live%20in%20our%20hearts%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%7BPhoto%20by%20Bishweshwar%20Das%7D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSGwpLp1uH5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSGwpLp1uH5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Red%20River%20(%40iwriteriot)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fiwriteriot%2Fstatus%2F1695999977728929836%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2028%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mahapatra%2C%20pain%20also%20proved%20to%20be%20generative%20and%20had%20helped%20him%20birth%20a%20poem%20he%20had%20cherished%20the%20most.%20The%20verses%20offered%20tribute%20to%20the%20memory%20of%20his%20grandparents%2C%20who%20had%20converted%20into%20Christianity%20as%20their%20world%20crumbled