20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693202195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28082709%2FUntitled-design-1-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fpoet-jayanta-mahapatra-passes-away-obituary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Considered%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20Indian%20poets%20in%20the%20English%20language%2C%20Mahapatra%20passed%20away%20in%20his%20hometown%20of%20Cuttack%20in%20Odisha%20at%20the%20age%20of%2095.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Neeraj%20Chopra%3A%20How%20A%20Chubby%20Kid%20From%20Haryana%20Transformed%20Into%20'Golden%20Boy'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20someone%20who%20was%20cajoled%20into%20taking%20up%20sport%20to%20shed%20weight%2C%20Neeraj%20Chopra's%20rise%20to%20stardom%20from%20a%20Haryana%20village%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20spectacular%2C%20and%20at%2025%2C%20he%20is%20already%20in%20the%20elite%20club%20of%20India's%20greatest%20sporting%20icons.%20Two%20years%20ago%2C%20his%20spear%20soared%20high%20into%20the%20Tokyo%20sky%20as%20he%20became%20the%20country's%20first%20Olympics%20track%20and%20field%20gold%20medal%20winner.%20He%20was%20just%2023%2C%20as%20he%20became%20only%20the%20second%20Indian%20to%20win%20an%20individual%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20Olympics%20after%20legendary%20shooter%20Abhinav%20Bindra.%20A%20star%20was%20born%20overnight%20in%20a%20country%20that%20had%20for%20long%20craved%20for%20the%20ultimate%20success%20in%20sport's%20biggest%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Bindra%2C%20who%20won%20the%2010m%20air%20rifle%20gold%20in%202008%20Beijing%20Olympics%2C%20India's%20eight%20other%20yellow%20metals%20at%20the%20Games%20had%20come%20from%20hockey%2C%20a%20team%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20gold%20medal%20on%20Sunday%20in%20the%20World%20Championships%2C%20the%20legend%20of%20Chopra%20continued%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20only%20the%20second%20Indian%20--%20again%20after%20Bindra%20--%20to%20simultaneously%20hold%20the%20Olympics%20and%20World%20Championships%20title.%20Bindra%20won%20the%20World%20Championships%20title%20when%20he%20was%2023%2C%20and%20the%20Olympics%20gold%20at%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20age%20on%20his%20side%2C%20Chopra%20is%20bound%20to%20achieve%20more%20success%20if%20he%20stays%20fit.%20He%20will%20have%20two%20Olympics%20and%20two%20World%20Championships%20before%20he%20turns%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperstardom%20after%20Tokyo%20gold%C2%A0%20The%20world%20junior%20championships%20triumph%20in%202016%20heralded%20Chopra's%20rise%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20but%20it%20was%20the%20gold%20in%20Tokyo%20in%202021%20that%20etched%20his%20name%20in%20Indian%20sporting%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20adulation%20showered%20on%20him%20was%20unprecedented%3B%20it%20was%20at%20par%20with%20if%20not%20more%20than%20some%20of%20the%20cricket%20icons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20toast%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20having%20attended%20so%20many%20felicitation%20programmes%20on%20one%20occasion%20exhaustion%20and%20fever%20forced%20him%20to%20leave%20a%20welcome%20function%20near%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20put%20on%20weight%20after%20missing%20training%20due%20to%20the%20many%20felicitation%20functions%20he%20had%20attended%20after%20the%20historic%20success%20in%20Tokyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20found%20himself%20among%20the%20most-searched%20Indian%20personalities%20online%20and%20ranked%20above%20the%20likes%20of%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20in%20Google%20searches%20in%20India.%20After%20his%20Tokyo%20triumph%2C%20Chopra's%20brand%20value%20skyrocketed%20with%20top%20brand%20sponsors%20lining%20up%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20brand%20value%20was%20compared%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Kohli%20and%20his%20Instagram%20and%20Twitter%20followers%20swelled%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Chopra%20dislodged%20the%20iconic%20world%20record%20holder%20sprinter%20Usain%20Bolt%20as%20the%20'most%20visible'%20and%20'written-about'%20athlete%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthletics%20Federation%20of%20India%20president%20Adille%20Sumariwalla%20said%20recently%20that%20Chopra's%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20gold%20has%20made%20parents%20think%20that%20there%20is%20a%20career%20beyond%20cricket%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumariwalla%20may%20not%20be%20off%20the%20mark%20as%20more%20than%20half%20a%20dozen%20Indians%20are%20currently%20capable%20of%20hurling%20the%20spear%20above%2080m%20and%20three%20Indians%2C%20including%20Chopra%2C%20featured%20in%20the%20World%20Championships%20men's%20javelin%20final%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAugust%207%2C%20the%20day%20Chopra%20won%20gold%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20is%20now%20being%20celebrated%20as%20National%20Javelin%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsistency%20is%20key%20for%20Chopra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsistency%20has%20been%20Chopra's%20forte%20since%20his%20Tokyo%20triumph%20as%20he%20has%20thrown%20above%2086m%20in%20all%20the%20events%20he%20has%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20Of%20course%2C%20he%20has%20not%20competed%20in%20too%20many%20competitions%20--%20just%20two%20this%20year%20before%20the%20World%20Championships%20--%20but%20there%20has%20not%20been%20any%20drop%20in%20his%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20least%20distance%20he%20has%20cleared%20since%20the%20Tokyo%20gold%20was%20the%2086.69m%20while%20winning%20the%20Kuortane%20Games%20title%20in%20Finland%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20His%20best%20is%20the%2089.94m%20which%20fetched%20him%20a%20second%20place%20at%20the%20Stockholm%20Diamond%20League%2C%20also%20in%20June%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20his%20closest%20competitors%20such%20as