day%2C%20the%2025-year-old%20ticked%20that%20milestone%20off%20too.%20While%20Neeraj%20finished%20top%20of%20the%20podium%2C%20it%20was%20Pakistan's%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20who%20bagged%20the%20second%20spot%2C%20taking%20home%20a%20silver%20medal.%20After%20the%20event%2C%20Neeraj%20opened%20up%20on%20how%20the%20Men's%20Javelin%20Throw%20final%20was%20perceived%2C%20especially%20back%20home%2C%20with%20the%20contest%20being%20dubbed%20as%20a%20battle%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20and%20Arshad%20have%20been%20competing%20with%20each%20other%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Whenever%20the%20two%20have%20taken%20to%20the%20field%20together%2C%20it's%20the%20Indian%20athlete%20who%20has%20come%20out%20on%20top.%20It%20was%20the%20same%20case%20in%20the%20World%20Athletics%20Championships%20where%20Neeraj%20emerged%20triumphant%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2088.17%20meters%20in%20the%20final.%20Nadeem%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20finished%20second%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2087.82%20meters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20use%20my%20mobile%20much%20before%20the%20competition%20but%20today%20I%20looked%20at%20it%20and%20the%20first%20thing%20was%20India%20versus%20Pakistan.%20But%20if%20you%20see%2C%20European%20athletes%20are%20very%20dangerous%20and%20at%20any%20time%20they%20can%20produce%20a%20big%20throw.%20Not%20just%20Arshad%2C%20there%20is%20Jakub%20and%20Julian%20Webber.%20So%20till%20the%20last%20throw%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20thinking%20about%20other%20throwers.%20But%20the%20thing%20is%20there%20will%20be%20India%20vs%20Pakistan%20comparisons%20back%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20event%20in%20Budapest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Asian%20Games%20being%20the%20next%20mega%20event%20where%20Arshad%20and%20Neeraj%20will%20be%20participating%2C%20the%20latter%20admitted%20that%20there%20will%20be%20more%20'India%20vs%20Pakistan'%20buzz%20in%20the%20continental%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games%20there%20will%20be%20more%20talk%20about%20India%20versus%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20I%20am%20just%20going%20to%20stay%20relaxed%20and%20healthy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20quite%20happy%20to%20see%20Arshad%20finish%20second%2C%20acknowledging%20how%20far%20both%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20come%20in%20the%20event%20that%20was%20traditionally%20dominated%20by%20the%20European%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20good%20that%20Arshad%20threw%20well%20and%20we%20discussed%20how%20both%20our%20countries%20are%20growing%20now.%20Earlier%20there%20were%20European%20athletes%20but%20now%20we%20have%20reached%20their%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693201920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fs88tqdj8_neeraj-chopra-afp_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Ffirst-thing-i-saw-was-neeraj-chopra-sums-up-india-vs-pakistan-buzz-in-javelin-throw-final-4334937%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neeraj%20Chopra%20and%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20finished%201-2%20in%20the%20Men's%20Javelin%20Throw%20final%20at%20the%20World%20Athletics%20Championships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A454%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Ffirst-thing-i-saw-was-neeraj-chopra-sums-up-india-vs-pakistan-buzz-in-javelin-throw-final-4334937%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Ffirst-thing-i-saw-was-neeraj-chopra-sums-up-india-vs-pakistan-buzz-in-javelin-throw-final-4334937%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Ffirst-thing-i-saw-was-neeraj-chopra-sums-up-india-vs-pakistan-buzz-in-javelin-throw-final-4334937%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20distributes%2051%2C000%20appointment%20letters%20under%20R