ts%20about%20the%20deceased%2C%20and%20they%20fought%20over%20it.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20this%20happened%20again%2C%20and%20he%20hit%20the%20woman%20with%20a%20cooker%2C%26quot%3B%20CK%20Baba%2C%20senior%20police%20officer%20of%20South%20Bengaluru%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaishnav%20was%20on%20the%20run%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20was%20caught.%20A%20murder%20case%20has%20been%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20arrested%20him%20and%20interrogation%20is%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693201140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Feo83e5so_pressure-cooker_625x300_16_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fman-arrested-for-killing-live-in-partner-with-pressure-cooker-in-bengaluru-4335192%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20police%20have%20arrested%20a%20man%20for%20allegedly%20beating%20his%20live-in%20partner%20to%20death%20with%20a%20pressure%20cooker%20because%20he%20suspected%20her%20of%20cheating%20on%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fman-arrested-for-killing-live-in-partner-with-pressure-cooker-in-bengaluru-4335192%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fman-arrested-for-killing-live-in-partner-with-pressure-cooker-in-bengaluru-4335192%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fman-arrested-for-killing-live-in-partner-with-pressure-cooker-in-bengaluru-4335192%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22''Worked%20Hard%20To%20Be%20Kind''%3A%20Indian-Origin%20CEO%20Who%20Fired%20900%20On%20Zoom%20Call%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20Vishal%20Garg%2C%20an%20Indian-origin%20chief%20executive%20of%20an%20online%20mortgage%20company%2C%20faced%20immense%20cri