expressed%20support%20for%20stronger%20cooperation%20and%20a%20more%20favorable%20policy%20environment.%20However%2C%20no%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20on%20disputes%20over%20technology%2C%20security%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20other%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftop-us-and-chinese-commerce-officials-express-support-for-better-trade-conditions%2Farticleshow%2F103118777.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftop-us-and-chinese-commerce-officials-express-support-for-better-trade-conditions%2Famp_articleshow%2F103118777.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftop-us-and-chinese-commerce-officials-express-support-for-better-trade-conditions%2Famp_articleshow%2F103118777.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Muslim%20Boy%20Slapped%20By%20Classmates%20On%20Teacher's%20Order%20Can't%20Sleep%3A%20Family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20student%2C%20who%20was%20slapped%20by%20his%20classmates%20following%20the%20orders%20of%20a%20school%20teacher%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20was%20taken%20to%20Meerut%20yesterday%20for%20a%20medical%20checkup%20after%20he%20complained%20of%20being%20disturbed%20and%20not%20able%20to%20sleep%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy's%20parents%20said%20that%20he%20has%20returned%20home%2C%20and%20is%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20complaining%20of%20being%20upset%20and%20not%20able%20to%20sleep%20throughout%20last%20night%2C%20the%20boy%20was%20brought%20to%20Meerut%20for%20a%20checkup.%20The%20doctor%20said%20that%20the%20boy%20was%20normal.%20He%20became%20disturbed%20due%20to%20several%20people%20including%20reporters%20asking%20him%20about%20the%20Neha%20Public%20School%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20father%20of%20the%20class%202%20student%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20a%20compromise%20with%20Tripta%20Tyagi%2C%20the%20school%20teacher%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20father%20said%20there%20will%20be%20no%20compromise%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20education%20department%20officials%20said%20the%20boy%20will%20be%20admitted%20to%20a%20government%20primary%20school%20provided%20his%20family%20agrees%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20will%20also%20facilitate%20the%20transfer%20of%20other%20students%20studying%20in%20Neha%20Public%20School%20in%20Khabbupur%20village%2C%20where%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Friday%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20father%20of%20the%20boy%20who%20was%20slapped%20does%20not%20want%20his%20son%20to%20continue%20his%20studies%20there%20(Neha%20Public%20School).%20The%20block%20education%20officer%20spoke%20to%20the%20boy%2C%20and%20he%20expressed%20his%20willingness%20to%20study%20in%20the%20government%20primary%20school%20in%20the%20village.%20On%20Monday%2C%20his%20enrolment%20will%20be%20done%20in%20the%20government%20school%2C%20provided%20his%20family%20is%20willing%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Muzaffarnagar%20Basic%20Shiksha%20Adhikari%20(BSA)%20Shubham%20Shukla%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20enrolment%20of%20the%20boy%20to%20a%20government%20school%2C%20his%20father%20said%20that%20the%20family%20has%20not%20decided%20about%20this%20as%20the%20boy%20is%20disturbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBSA%20Shukla%20said%20that%20the%20private%20school%20in%20Khabbupur%20village%20will%20not%20be%20closed%20and%20normal%20teaching%20activities%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20school%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20give%20in%20a%20month%20its%20clarification%20to%20the%20department%20regarding%20its%20affiliation.%20It%20has%20three%20teachers%20and%20runs%20classes%20from%20one%20to%20five%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BSA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20Public%20School%20is%20affiliated%20to%20the%20basic%20education%20department%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government.%20Currently%2C%2050%20students%20study%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20school%20teacher%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20will%20continue%20teaching%20in%20the%20school%2C%20Mr%20Shukla%20said%20that%20it%20depends%20on%20police%20action%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSA%20also%20said%20that%20the%20block%20education%20officer%20will%20go%20to%20Neha%20Public%20School%20on%20Monday%20and%20make%20arrangements%20for%20those%20students%20who%20want%20to%20come%20there%20for%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20government%20primary%20school%20in%20the%20village.%20Children%20who%20want%20to%20go%20there%20will%20be%20enrolled%20there.%20Students%2C%20who%20wish%20to%20continue%20study%20in%20the%20private%20school%2C%20can%20do%20so%20since%20they%20are%20already%20paying%20the%20fees.%20The%20formalities%20including%20transfer%20certificates%20(of%20the%20children)%20will%20be%20completed%20by%20the%20department%2C%20so%20that%20the%20parents%20do%20not%20face%20any%20additional%20burden%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BSA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20outrage%20poured%20in%20from%20all%20quarters%2C%20police%20on%20Saturday%20booked%20Tripta%20Tyagi%2C%20the%20school%20teacher%20accused%20of%20making%20communal%20comments%20and%20ordering%20her%20students%20to%20slap%20a%20Muslim%20classmate%20for%20not%20doing%20his%20homework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20was%20also%20served%20a%20notice%20by%20the%20education%20department%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20booked%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20boy's%20family%20under%20IPC%20sections%20323%20(punishment%20for%20voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%20and%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20the%20peace)%20--%20both%20non-cognizable%20offences.%20Such%20offences%20are%20bailable%20and%20do%20not%20l