e%20said.%20His%20sister%20was%20also%20beaten%20and%20his%20mother%20was%20stripped%20naked%20when%20she%20tried%20to%20save%20her%20son%20from%20the%20attackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine%20people%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20murder%20and%20three%20will%20face%20charges%20under%20the%20stringent%20Scheduled%20Caste%2FScheduled%20Tribes%20Act.%20Eight%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20informed%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Sanjeev%20Uikey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2018-year-old%20victim's%20sister%20alleged%20some%20people%20were%20pressuring%20her%20to%20withdraw%20her%20case%20and%20this%20led%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20thrashed%20him%20a%20lot.%20He%20couldn't%20survive.%3Cem%3E%20Hume%20beparda%20kar%20diya.%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20was%20stripped.%20Then%20the%20cops%20arrived%20and%20I%20was%20handed%20a%20towel.%20I%20stood%20there%20in%20a%20towel%20until%20they%20got%20me%20a%20saree%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20young%20man's%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20mob%20also%20ransacked%20and%20vandalized%20their%20home.%20%26quot%3BNone%20of%20the%20household%20items%20are%20left%20intact.%20Even%20the%20pucca%20roofs%20were%20broken%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20they%20went%20to%20another%20house%20in%20search%20of%20her%20other%20two%20sons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20aunt%20said%20a%20mob%20barged%20into%20her%20house%20too%20and%20threatened%20her%20husband%20and%20children.%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20have%20killed%20my%20children%20and%20husband%20too.%20They%20even%20checked%20our%20fridge%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20remains%20tense%20in%20the%20village%20with%20heavy%20police%20force%20deployed%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20family%20performed%20his%20final%20rites%20after%20the%20district%20collector%20assured%20them%20of%20help%20under%20government%20schemes%20and%20informed%20them%20of%20the%20arrests%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20victim's%20sister%20had%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20four%20men%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20threatening%20and%20beating%20her.%20All%20four%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20that%20is%20now%20in%20the%20courts%2C%20said%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20triggered%20a%20political%20row%20in%20election-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20and%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20slamming%20the%20BJP%20government.%20The%20ruling%20party%20said%20prompt%20action%20was%20taken%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20adopting%20a%20selective%20approach%20on%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20Dalit%20and%20tribal%20oppression%20continued%20unabated%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20is%20due%20for%20polls%20this%20yearend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20the%20state%20has%20the%20highest%20rate%20of%20crimes%20against%20Dalits%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20BJP%20has%20made%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20a%20laboratory%20of%20Dalit%20atrocities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%20demanded%20financial%20assistance%20for%20the%20victim's%20family%20and%20claimed%20the%20accused%20had%20links%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Minister%20Bhupendra%20Singh%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20claiming%20the%20crime%20was%20a%20fallout%20of%20a%20dispute.%20He%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20politicising%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20secretary%20Rajneesh%20Agrawal%20told%20PTI%20his%20party's%20government%20acted%20promptly%20in%20the%20case%20whereas%20Congress%20governments%20didn't%20even%20bother%20to%20take%20action%20in%20cases%20of%20Dalit%20atrocities%20in%20states%20governed%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693193760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fd4s0kufg_mp-d