rtunity%26quot%3B%20on%20January%206%2C%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERamaswamy%20said%20on%20NBC's%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20Pence%20should%20have%20sought%20major%20election%20reforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Pence%20campaign%20on%20Sunday%20blasted%20Ramaswamy's%20comments%20as%20%26quot%3Bshocking%20and%20concerning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERepublican%20presidential%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20former%20Vice%20President%20Mike%20Pence%20missed%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20sweeping%20election%20changes%20on%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20before%20certifying%20the%202020%20presidential%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fmeet-the-press%2Fvideo%2Framaswamy-says-he-would-ve-certified-2020-election-but-pence-missed-historic-opportunity-191684165571%5C%22%3EDuring%20an%20appearance%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20NBC's%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramaswamy%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20entrepreneur%20and%20first-time%20political%20candidate%2C%20said%20that%20he%20would%20have%20taken%20a%20different%20approach%20to%20the%20election%20certification%20had%20he%20been%20in%20Pence's%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20have%20done%20it%20very%20differently.%20I%20think%20that%20there%20was%20a%20historic%20opportunity%20that%20he%20missed%2C%20to%20reunite%20this%20country%20in%20that%20window%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20would%20have%20said%20is%3A%20This%20is%20a%20moment%20for%20a%20true%20national%20consensus%20where%20there's%20two%20elements%20of%20what's%20required%20for%20a%20functioning%20democracy%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BOne%20is%20secure%20elections%2C%20and%20the%20second%20is%20a%20peaceful%20transfer%20of%20power.%20When%20those%20things%20come%20into%20conflict%2C%20that's%20an%20opportunity%20for%20heroism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%