.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flier%2C%20which%20says%20that%20%26quot%3Bsome%20Yalies%20do%20manage%20to%20survive%20New%20Haven%20and%20even%20retain%20their%20personal%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20points%20to%20crime%20statistics%20in%20the%20New%20England%20city%20that%20university%20officials%20insist%20is%20misleading%20and%20a%20tactic%20that%20the%20union%20is%20employing%20as%20it%20seeks%20a%20new%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20instructs%20students%20to%20%26quot%3Bremain%20on%20campus%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bavoid%20public%20transportation%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bstay%20off%20the%20streets%20after%208%20p.m.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPosted%20near%20the%20top%20of%20the%20flier%20is%20an%20illustration%20of%20the%20Grim%20Reaper%20with%20a%20pointed%20message%3A%20%26quot%3BGood%20luck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gawker.com%2Ffear-city-the-insane-pamphlet-the-nypd-used-to-terrori-1678292956%5C%22%3EThe%20Yale%20fliers%20are%20similar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BWelcome%20to%20Fear%20City%26quot%3B%20fliers%20given%20to%20tourists%20visiting%20New%20York%20City%20in%20the%201970s%20%E2%80%94%20when%20the%20city%20struggled%20with%20violent%20crime%20%E2%80%94%20which%20directed%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bstay%20off%20the%20streets%20after%206%20p.m.%26quot%3B%20and%20call%20for%20cabs%20in%20lieu%20of%20walking%20outside%20in%20the%20evenings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Campbell%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Yale%20Police%20Department%20and%20the%20onetime%20police%20chief%20of%20New%20Haven%2C%20blasted%20the%20police%20union%20over%20its%20message%20to%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20extremely%20hurt%20and%20sad%20and%20disgusted%20by%20the%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20Yale%20Police%20Benevolent%20Association%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F25%2Fnyregion%2Fyale-police-fliers.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20is%20divisive%20and%20destructive%20for%20any%20police%20officer%20to%20disparage%20the%20city%20in%20which%20they%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20in%20its%20flier%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3Bmurders%20have%20doubled%2C%20burglaries%20are%20up%2033%20percent%20and%20motor%20vehicle%20thefts%20are%20up%2056%20percent%26quot%3B%20through%20the%20end%20of%20July.%20(According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newhavenct.gov%2Fhome%2Fshowpublisheddocument%2F19475%2F638259907631230000%5C%22%3Eofficial%20New%20Haven%20crime%20statistics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20numbers%20are%20accurate%2C%20with%20burglaries%20up%20from%20177%20last%20year%20to%20235%20through%20July%2023%20and%20car%20thefts%20having%20risen%20from%20390%20last%20year%20to%20609%20through%20July%2023.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20violent%20crime%20has%20declined%20by%2016.2%25%20through%20July%2023%2C%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20violent%20crime%20has%20also%20dropped%20by%2029.2%25%20since%202020%2C%20New%20Haven%20Mayor%20Justin%20Elicker%20has%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%20or%20so%2C%20crime%20is%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Elicker%20told%20The%20Times.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20actual%20numbers%20may%20be%20accurate%2C%20they%20don't%20present%20the%20full%20picture%20of%20what's%20going%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Matthews%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20the%20Yale%20police%20union%20and%20a%20former%20Yale%20Police%20Department%20officer%2C%20said%20that%20the%20flier%20was%20not%20being%20used%20as%20leverage%20in%20the%20union's%20contract%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20there%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20fearmonger%20or%20scare%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20The%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20that%20the%20officers%20wanted%20to%20leave%20an%20impression%20with%20students%20amid%20all%20the%20other%20messages%20that%20they%20would%20receive%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20without%20a%20doubt%2C%20their%20pamphlet%20stands%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Campbell%2C%20the%20Yale%20police%20chief%2C%20reiterated%20to%20the%20newspaper%20that%20he%20disagreed%20with%20the%20sort%20of%20impression%20that%20the%20flier%20was%20generating%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%2C%20from%20the%20day%20you're%20moving%20in%2C%20that%20the%20police%20department%20doesn't%20have%20its%20house%20in%20order%2C%20then%20you%20start%20saying%3A%20'Well%2C%20can%20I%20even%20count%20on%20you%20to%20tell%20me%20the%20truth%20and%20to%20really%20keep%20me%20safe%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyale-police-union-crime-grim-reaper-fliers-new-haven-students-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693166064000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e6fd942c4854076353ac0f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyale-police-union-crime-grim-reaper-fliers-new-haven-students-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anthony%20Campbell%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Yale%20Police%20Department%20and%20the%20ex-New%20Haven%20police%20chief%2C%20blasted%20the%20union's%20fliers%20as%20%26quot%3Bdivisive%20and%20destructive.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyale-police-union-crime-grim-reaper-fliers-new-haven-students-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20asked%20people%20in%20Madrid%20what%20they%20thought%20of%20World%20Cup%20kiss%20row%20-%20their%20response%20was%20'eye-opening'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693164540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http