22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuzaffarnagar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Following%20the%20video%20of%20a%20teacher%20egging%20on%20her%20students%20to%20hit%20their%20seven-year-old%20Muslim%20classmate%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20journalists%20and%20politicians%20made%20a%20beeline%20to%20the%20remote%20Khubbapur%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Muzaffarnagar%20the%20next%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20one%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20who%20runs%20the%20Neha%20Public%20School%20at%20her%20home%20can%20be%20seen%20exhorting%20the%20students%20to%20assault%20a%20child%20who%20is%20seen%20crying%20while%20different%20students%20come%20forward%C2%A0%20to%20slap%20him.%20At%20one%20point%20in%20the%20video%2C%20the%20teacher%20scolded%20a%20student%20for%20not%20hitting%20him%20hard%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20declared%20that%20all%20those%20Muslim%20children%20should%20be%E2%80%A6(inaudible)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20forty-second%20long%20video.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reached%20the%20village%2C%20its%20dilapidated%20roads%20were%20jammed%20with%20SUVs.%20Surrounded%20by%20large%20belts%20of%20sugarcane%20farms%2C%20Khubbapur%20is%20predominantly%20inhabited%20by%20people%20from%20the%20Tyagi%20caste%20who%20are%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20this%20reporter%20could%20ask%20any%20questions%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20a%20group%20of%20Muslim%20villagers%20outside%20the%20narrow%20street%20leading%20to%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20home%20declared%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccompromise%20has%20been%20reached.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20that%20pressure%20is%20mounting%20on%20the%20family%20to%20settle%20the%20matter%20and%20quoted%20a%20village%20leader%20warning%20the%20family%20to%20quash%20the%20FIR%20or%20face%20consequences.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Th%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ee%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Emet%20Irshad%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20victim%20who%20we%20spoke%20to%20a%20night%20earlier%20over%20call%2C%20he%20was%20already%20being%20interviewed%20by%20a%20Youtuber%20who%20was%20trying%20to%20tutor%20Irshad%20to%20say%20what%20he%20wanted.%20When%20we%20finally%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20speak%20with%20him%2C%20he%20was%20surrounded%20by%20over%20a%20dozen%20people.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20such%20an%20incident%20had%20happened%20but%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20attention%20because%20teachers%20hit%20students%20when%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20schoolwork%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20But%20he%20was%20stunned%20after%20watching%20the%20video.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20Muzaffarnagar%20village%2C%20pressure%20on%20family%20of%20child%20who%20was%20slapped%20after%20goading%20by%20teacher%20to%20%E2%80%98compromise%E2%80%99%20.%20No%20surprise%20then%20that%20videos%20are%20being%20put%20out%20by%20RW%20handles%20to%20water%20down%20the%20case.%20What%20teacher%20said%20on%20camera%20is%20for%20all%20to%20see%3A%20don%E2%80%99t%20defend%20the%20indefensible.%20Act%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Rajdeep%20Sardesai%20(%40sardesairajdeep)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsardesairajdeep%2Fstatus%2F1695494465643811071%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Irshad%20confronted%20the%20teacher%2C%20she%20allegedly%20threatened%20him.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20I%20decided%20to%20cancel%20my%20child%E2%80%99s%20admission%20and%20have%20stopped%20sending%20him%20to%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reiterated%20his%20stance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20teacher%20is%20said%20to%20have%20%E2%80%98apologised%E2%80%99%20to%20Irshad%20and%20promised%20that%20such%20an%20incident%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20repeated.%20Irshad%20reportedly%20agreed%20to%20not%20take%20the%20matter%20any%20further.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20day%20later%20the%20right-wing%20ran%20hashtags%20in%20her%20support%20and%20the%20teacher%20told%20the%20press%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20not%20ashamed%20of%20what%20happened.%20Irshad%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20said%20that%20the%20matter%20should%20not%20be%20looked%20at%20with%20a%20communal%20lens%20and%20the%20teacher%20was%20talking%20about%20%E2%80%9CMohammedan%20mothers%20taking%20their%20children%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20that%20affects%20their%20education.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20speaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20he%20demanded%20justice%20and%20stressed%20on%20legal%20action%20but%20in%20some%20other%20reports%20he%E2%80%99s%20also%20said%20that%20wants%20to%20end%20the%20matter.%20This%20was%20also%20the%20larger%20focus%20of%20influential%20leaders%20and%20politicians%20meeting%20the%20family%20who%20kept%20stressing%20on%20making%20%E2%80%9Ca%20compromise%E2%80%9D%20and%20maintaining%20the%20peace%20and%20harmony%20between%20the%20two%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFarmer%20Naresh%20Tikait%20met%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20told%20the%20media%20that%20he%E2%80%99ll%20get%20the%20FIR%20expunged.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFaisla%20ho%20gaya%20gaya%20hai%E2%80%A6FIR%20hatwa%20denge%E2%80%A6Maari%20itni%20bhi%20na%20chale%20kya%20iss%20zile%20mein%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(It%20has%20been%20decided%20that%20the%20FIR%20will%20be%20taken%20back.%20I%20hold%20that%20much%20influence%20in%20the%20area)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20both%20parties%20are%20%E2%80%9Csatisfied%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Shrikant%20Tyagi%2C%20the%20former%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leader%2C%20who%20had%20hit%20the%20headlines%20for%20abusing%20a%20woman%20at%20a%20gated%20society%20in%20Noida%2C%20came%20to%20meet%20the%20family%20and%20the%20teacher.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20brotherhood%20between%20Tyagis%20(Muslims%20and%20Hindus)%20who%20are%20from%20the%20same%20family%20is%20being%20harmed%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20because%20of%20the%202024%20elections.%E2%80%9D%20On%20his%20Facebook%20page%2C%20he%20posted%20pictures%20with%20both%20sides%20and%20appealed%20that%20the%20matter%20should%20be%20settled%20amicably%20and%20the%20child%20should%20continue%20his%20education%20in%20the%20same%20school.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20a%20source%20(another%20minor)%20said%20that%20he%20was%20also%20assaulted%20by%20the%20teacher%20in%20a%20similar%20manner%20and%20that%20the%20teacher%20only%20targets%20Muslim%20students%2C%20Irshad%E2%80%99s%20neighbour%20Rizwan%20immediately%20refuted%20him%20and%20said%20that%20the%20teacher%20should%20not%20have%20done%20this%20but%20all%20children%20get%20beaten%20up%20at%20schools.%20He%20declined%20any%20communal%20angle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20tried%20to%20contact%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20but%20the%20crowd%20of%20mostly%20Tyagis%20outside%20her%20house%20said%20that%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20meet%20her%20since%20%E2%80%9Cshe%20is%20not%20at%20home%E2%80%9D.%20The%20crowd%20said%20that%20a%20small%20matter%20was%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion%20by%20the%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20Rahul%20Tyagi%20(38)%2C%20a%20sugarcane%20farmer%2C%20said%20that%20city%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20village%20lingo%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20common%20practice%20to%20refer%20to%20people%20with%20their%20caste%20names.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20done%20out%20of%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20bystander%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20village%20people%20are%20simple%3B%20they%20call%20brahmins%20as%20brahmins%20and%20Nai%20as%20Nai.%20This%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etheth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(local)%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rahul.%20He%20emphasised%20that%20the%20teacher%20calling%20a%20student%20by%20his%20caste%20or%20religion%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20big%20deal.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20people%20talk%20in%20the%20whole%20country.%20Here%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20still%20call%20people%20as%20Chowdhury%20%3Cem%3Esahab%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Yadav%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20if%20we%20go%20to%20Rajasthan%2C%20there%2C%20they%20will%20simply%20use%20the%20caste.%20This%20happens%20everywhere%20but%20it%20got%20such%20traction.%20They%20have%20no%20prior%20rivalry.%20Everyone%20is%20Tyagi%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693134401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20233349%2FIMG_0509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-pressure-on-boys-family-to-compromise-in-slapping-incident-as-politicians-swarm-the-village%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmer%20Naresh%20Tikait%20met%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20told%20the%20media%20that%20he'll%20get%20the%20FIR%20registered%20against%20the%20teacher%20expunged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A57%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-pressure-on-boys-family-to-compromise-in-slapping-incident-as-politicians-swarm-the-village%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Sets%20up%20Inquiry%20Commission%20to%20Probe%20%E2%80%9840%25%20Commission%E2%80%99%20Allegations%20During%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18164526%2FFwBN2HcakAEGvBw.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20notified%20the%20formation%20of%20an%20inquiry%20commission%20to%20investigate%20allegations%20of%20%E2%80%9840%25%20commission%E2%80%99%20for%20projects%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20power%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-govt-forms-probe-team-to-inquire-40-commission-allegation-against-bjp-2662229%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20had%20run%20a%20successful%20campaign%20to%20win%20the%20state%20assembly%20election%20earlier%20based%20on%20the%20allegations%20made%20in%20a%20letter%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20Contractors%20Association%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20association%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20contractors%20had%20to%20agree%20to%20pay%20a%2025-30%25%20cut%20before%20the%20start%20of%20civil%20works%20and%205-6%25%20for%20post-work%20bills.%20They%20had%20also%20complained%20that%20the%20guidelines%20favoured%20contractors%20from%20outside%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government%20had%20earlier%20issued%20a%20notification%20setting%20up%20a%20one-man%20committee%20headed%20by%20retired%20High%20Court%20Justice%20H.N.%20Nagamohan%20Das%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20latest%20notification%20of%20an%20inquiry%20commission%2C%20the%20earlier%20order%20has%20been%20annulled.%20Justice%20Das%20would%20still%20head%20the%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-govt-forms-probe-team-to-inquire-40-commission-allegation-against-bjp-2662229%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20government%20decided%20to%20form%20a%20commission%20instead%20of%20a%20committee%20in%20order%20to%20give%20more%20teeth%20to%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9C40%25%20commission%E2%80%9D%20allegation%20that%20eventually%20led%20to%20the%20defeat%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20the%20commission%20has%20been%20constituted%20under%20the%20Commissions%20of%20Inquiry%20Act%20whereas%20the%20previous%20committee%20was%20formed%20by%20way%20of%20an%20executive%20order%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20objective%20of%20the%20commission%20is%20to%20examine%20the%20assertions%20made%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20State%20Contractors%20Association.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20commission%20will%20delve%20into%20any%20shortcomings%20in%20the%20tender%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693133235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18164526%2FFwBN2HcakAEGvBw.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-sets-up-inquiry-commission-to-probe-40-commission-allegations-during-bjps-rule%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20commission%20will%20delve%20into%20any%20shortcomings%20in%20the%20tender%20procedures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A73%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-sets-up-inquiry-commission-to-probe-40-commission-allegations-during-bjps-rule%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20campaign%20raises%20%247.1m%20following%20historic%20Georgia%20mugshot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693132526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FCD97%2Fpro