20of%20ports%20in%20Greece%2C%20while%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20was%20fully%20aware%20of%20this%20issue%20caused%20an%20impression.%20After%20all%2C%20there%20was%20also%20the%20first%20allusion%20to%20a%20deal%20of%20Indian%20dimensions%20that%20the%20vast%20country%20wishes%20to%20make%3A%20The%20reason%20for%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20Indian%20group%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20billionaire%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani%20(richest%20Asian%20and%20until%20last%20year%20number%20two%20on%20the%20list%20of%20Forbes%20with%20the%20richest%20people%20on%20the%20planet)%20for%20the%20acquisition%20of%20a%20port%20in%20Greece.%20Adani%2C%20according%20to%20what%20has%20become%20known%2C%20has%20focused%20on%20two%20ports%3A%20Primarily%20that%20of%20Kavala%20and%20secondarily%20that%20of%20Volos%2C%20while%20he%20is%20also%20interested%20in%20Alexandroupoli.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20focus%20of%20the%20India-Greece%20partnership%20is%20initially%20on%20defence%2C%20%3Cem%3EFree%20Press%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Findia%2Fpm-narendra-modi-strikes-another-strategic-partnership-this-time-with-greece%5C%22%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20took%20part%20in%20a%20European%20military%20exercise%20staged%20in%20Greece%20this%20spring%2C%20while%20India%20and%20Greece%20held%20a%20combined%20naval%20exercise%20in%20Crete.%20Furthermore%2C%20Greek%20fighter%20jets%20are%20expected%20to%20take%20part%20in%20an%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20drill%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20Modi%20highlighted%20the%20goal%20of%20doubling%20bilateral%20trade%20by%202030%20and%20announced%20an%20agreement%20in%20the%20field%20of%20agricultural%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGreek%20City%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreekcitytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F26%2Fport-acquisitions-indian-tourists%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20M