20nothingness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20welcome%20compensation%20for%20loss%2C%20poetry%20navigates%20around%20the%20sharp%20edges%20of%20life%20without%20underprizing%20it.%20Its%20potency%20and%20universal%20appeal%20is%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98tremor%20and%20draw%E2%80%99%20of%20words%20that%20please%20the%20senses%20and%20arouse%20the%20spirit.%20The%20expression%20of%20intense%20sensitivity%20anchored%20in%20the%20pulsating%20vibrance%20of%20rhyming%20words%20enhances%20its%20appeal.%20Its%20lyrical%20pull%20magnifies%20the%20force%20of%20the%20message%20of%20togetherness%2C%20compassion%2C%20justice%20and%20injustice%2C%20love%20and%20hate%2C%20identity%20and%20difference%2C%20submission%20and%20assertion%2C%20anger%20and%20anguish%20et%20al%2C%20in%20a%20symphony%20of%20life%E2%80%99s%20many%20hues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPoetry%20creates%20its%20own%20music%20and%20is%20about%20moments%20in%20life%20with%20which%20it%20is%20entwined.%20It%20assembles%20%E2%80%9Clanguage%20into%20art%E2%80%9D%20freeing%20the%20poet%20to%20be%20both%20%E2%80%9Cdignified%20and%20bold%E2%80%9D.%20It%20%E2%80%9Cfills%20the%20air%2C%20rustles%20the%20leaves%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20poet%20weaves%20the%20truth%20of%20his%20age%20in%20the%20image%20of%20his%20own%20experiences.%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%E2%80%99s%20introduction%20to%20his%20poetry%20says%20it%20all%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cduniy%C4%81%20ne%20tajrab%C4%81t%20o%20hav%C4%81dis%20k%C4%AB%20shakl%20me%C3%B1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejo%20kuchh%20mujhe%20diy%C4%81%20hai%2C%20vo%20lauT%C4%81%20rah%C4%81%20huu%C3%B1%20main%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5B%E2%80%9CWhatever%20the%20world%20has%20given%20to%20me%20by%20way%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eexperience%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20accident%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20what%20I%20am%20returning%E2%80%9D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soul%20of%20the%20author%20is%20laid%20bare%20in%20his%20poetry%20%E2%80%93%20a%20%E2%80%98voice%20that%20survives%20the%20silencing%20of%20the%20voice%E2%80%99.%20Inspired%20by%20compelling%20emotions%20and%20sheltered%20in%20the%20depth%20of%20private%20spaces%2C%20poetry%2C%20as%20an%20expression%20of%20the%20self%2C%20is%20profoundly%20personal.%20Its%20popular%20resonance%20is%20a%20function%20of%20the%20common%20truths%20that%20it%20mirrors%2C%20of%20which%20Seemab%20Akbarabadi%20has%20famously%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ckah%C4%81n%C4%AB%20mer%C4%AB%20r%C5%ABd%C4%81d-e-jah%C4%81%C3%B1%20maal%C5%ABm%20hot%C4%AB%20hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejo%20sunt%C4%81%20hai%20us%C4%AB%20k%C4%AB%20d%C4%81st%C4%81%C3%B1%20maal%C5%ABm%20hot%C4%AB%20hai%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5B%E2%80%9CMy%20story%20is%20the%20story%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20who%20hears%20it%2C%20considers%20it%20his%20own.%E2%80%9D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20poet%E2%80%99s%20function%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20his%20own%20reality%20and%20that%20of%20the%20world%20around%20him%20does%20not%20remain%20outside%20the%20poetic%20realm.%20His%20canvas%20is%20broad%20enough%20to%20hold%20the%20many%20colours%20of%20life%20in%20a%20natural%20coalescence.%20He%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98philosopher%20of%20the%20heart%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20chronicler%20of%20the%20past%2C%20purveyor%20of%20the%20present%20and%20projector%20of%20the%20future.%20His%20vision%20bears%20the%20imprint%20of%20lived%20experiences%20and%20bridges%20the%20divide%20between%20sentiment%20and%20life%E2%80%99s%20reality.%20Shakeel%20Badayuni%20brings%20out%20the%20interface%20between%20life%20and%20literature%20thus%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EM%C4%93n%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShakeel%2C%20Dil%20Ka%20Hoon%20Tarjuma%2C%20Ki%20Mohabbaton%20Ka%20Hoon%20Raazdaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMujhe%20Fakhr%20Hai%20Meri%20Shayari%2C%20Meri%20Zindagi%C2%A0Se%C2%A0Juda%C2%A0Nahi%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5B%20Shakeel%2C%20I%20am%20but%20an%20echo%20of%20my%20heart%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20confidante%20of%20the%20emotion%20of%20love%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20proud%2C%20my%20poetry%20and%20life%20are%20not%20apart.%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20wider%20philosophical%20imagination%2C%20the%20litterateurs%20interrogate%20the%20injustices%20of%20the%20times%20%E2%80%98in%20the%20still%20sad%20music%20of%20humanity.%E2%80%99%20Whether%20in%20depicting%20despair%2C%20ecstasy%20of%20the%20pain%20of%20unrequited%20love%2C%20hopelessness%2C%20the%20romanticism%20of%20protest%20or%20heroism%20of%20the%20brave%2C%20all%20have%20found%20immortality%20in%20literature.%20So%20it%20is%20that%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20histories%20of%20the%20Age%20and%20nations%20are%20encased%20in%20their%20literature%20that%20clothes%20the%20bones%20of%20history%20in%20the%20culture%20of%20our%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20uniting%20philosophy%2C%20feeling%20and%20verve%2C%20art%20keeps%20alive%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20ages%20that%20shows%20us%20the%20way.%20Bertolt%20Brecht%20reminded%20us%20that%20art%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20a%20mirror%20held%20up%20to%20reality%20but%20a%20hammer%20with%20which%20to%20shape%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Treasured%20compositions%20of%20the%20masters%20that%20encase%20profound%20wisdom%20and%20sensibilities%20of%20their%20time%20in%20the%20sublime%20arrangement%20of%20words%2C%20define%20for%20us%20our%20humanity%2C%20giving%20us%20the%20music%20of%20our%20lives%20and%20the%20light%20that%20brightens%20our%20path.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll