Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20poet%E2%80%99s%20recall%20of%20the%20eternal%20dilemma%20of%20a%20finite%20life%20and%20its%20infinite%20obligations%20is%20compelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAahista%20chal%20zindagi%2C%20abhi%20kai%20karz%20chukana%20baaki%20hai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKuch%20dard%20mitana%20baaki%20hai%2C%20Kuch%20farz%20nibhana%20baaki%20hai%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5BSlow%20down%2C%20Oh%20life!%20Many%20debts%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20paid%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20pain%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20erased%20and%20duties%20discharged.%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20product%20of%20his%20environment%20in%20a%20dialectical%20relationship%2C%20the%20poet%E2%80%99s%20lament%2C%20advisories%20and%20admonitions%2C%20even%20when%20expressed%20in%20personal%20terms%2C%20have%20a%20larger%20message%20in%20a%20broader%20social%20and%20political%20context.%20The%20philosopher%20in%20the%20poet%20is%20thus%20an%20agent%20of%20progressive%C2%A0change.%20Because%20the%20power%20of%20expression%20defines%20the%20measure%20of%20the%20message%20itself%2C%20the%20emotion%20of%20our%20freedom%20struggle%20was%20captured%20in%20the%20gems%20of%20literature%20which%20are%20now%20a%20part%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20political%20folklore%20and%20inspiration%20for%20a%20continuing%20struggle%20against%20injustice%20and%20oppression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBankim%20Chandra%20Chatterjee%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Vande%20Mataram%E2%80%99%2C%20Bismil%20Azimabadi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Sarfaroshi%20ki%20Tamanna%E2%80%99%20and%20Ram%20Prasad%20Bismil%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Mera%20Rang%20De%20Basanti%20Chola%E2%80%99%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20spirit%20of%20freedom%20without%20bitterness%20and%20hatred%20for%20the%20colonial%20masters%2C%20galvanized%20the%20entire%20nation%20to%20attain%20independence.%20Such%20is%20the%20power%20of%20these