%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emai%C3%B1%20tumh%C4%81r%C4%81%20huu%C3%B1%20luTero%C3%B1%20k%C4%81%20vaf%C4%81d%C4%81r%20nah%C4%AB%C3%B1%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5B%E2%80%9CBut%20O%20golden%20dreams%20of%20human%20pride%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20not%20a%20worshiper%20of%20royal%20glory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20(mankind)%20are%20the%20essence%20of%20my%20thoughts%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20yours%2C%20my%20loyalty%20is%20not%20for%20the%20exploiters.%E2%80%9D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPravin%20Shakir%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20lament%20against%20oppression%20must%20weigh%20with%20every%20sensitive%20soul%20and%20serves%20as%20an%20inspiration%20for%20our%20collective%20pursuit%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cp%C4%81-ba-gil%20sab%20hai%C3%B1%20rih%C4%81.%C4%AB%20k%C4%AB%20kare%20tadb%C4%ABr%20kaun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edast-basta%20shahr%20me%C3%B1%20khole%20mir%C4%AB%20zanj%C4%ABr%20kaun%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emer%C4%81%20sar%20h%C4%81zir%20hai%20lekin%20mer%C4%81%20munsif%20dekh%20le%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekar%20rah%C4%81%20hai%20mer%C4%AB%20fard-e-jurm%20ko%20tahr%C4%ABr%20kaun%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5B%E2%80%9CWho%20can%20devise%20a%20plan%20for%20my%20liberation%2C%20with%20feet%20in%20chains%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWho%20can%20unlock%20my%20shackles%20in%20this%20confined%20city%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20head%20is%20for%20you%20to%20take%2C%20but%20let%20my%20judge%20see%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWho%20my%20prosecutor%20is.%E2%80%9D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsrarul%20Haq%20Majaz%E2%80%99s%20exposition%20of%20resolute%20will%20to%20pursue%20a%20larger%20cause%20ret