stand%20aside.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20getting%20annoyed%2C%20Vikrambhai%20gathered%20us%20close%20to%20the%20balloon%2C%20explained%20its%20mechanics%2C%20and%20told%20us%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20meteorological%20data%20it%20would%20be%20gathering%20in%20the%20lower%20atmosphere.%20Such%20data%20was%20being%20collected%20for%20the%20first%20time%20by%20India.%20We%20watched%20the%20ascent%20with%20great%20awe%20and%20our%20curiosity%20showed%20no%20signs%20of%20abating%20and%20even%20as%20the%20light%20began%20to%20fade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20350px)%2085vw%2C%20350px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F27132157%2FSarabhai.jpg.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F27132157%2FSarabhai.jpg.jpeg%20350w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F27132157%2FSarabhai.jpg-233x300.jpeg%20233w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670060%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EISRO%20founder%20Vikram%20Sarabhai.%20Photo%3A%20isro.gov.in%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20peppered%20the%20scientists%20with%20questions%20on%20all%20sorts%20of%20scientific%20and%20not-so-scientific%20matters%20that%20only%20children%20are%20capable%20of%20asking.%20How%20long%20would%20the%20balloon%20stay%20up%3F%20Could%20one%20accidentally%20drift%20away%20into%20space%3F%20Wouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%20be%20fun%20to%20go%20up%20with%20one%20to%20chase%20the%20weather%2C%20enter%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20overlook%20cities%3F%20And%20as%20the%20moon%20rose%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20we%20discussed%20the%20moon%2C%20and%20rockets%2C%20and%20wondered%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20you%20threw%20an%20apple%20from%20the%20window%20of%20your%20rocket%20in%20space%20and%20if%20it%20would%20land%20on%20earth%20as%20Newton%20promised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVikrambhai%20and%20the%20other%20scientists%20welcomed%20our%20flights%20of%20fancy%2C%20mostly%20encouraging%20us%20to%20answer%20our%20own%20questions%20based%20on%20the%20scientific%20principles%20we%20already%20knew%2C%20and%20at%20other%20times%20telling%20us%20about%20astonishing%20new%20discoveries%20that%20pushed%20the%20boundaries%20of%20human%20knowledge.%20It%20was%20a%20night%20of%20wonder%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evismay%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(astonishment)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eyoung%20and%20the%20old%2C%20of%20knowing%20and%20discovering%2C%20of%20science%20and%20fantasy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20young%20minds%20were%20full%20of%20burning%20questions.%20Those%20among%20us%20with%20a%20scientific%20bent%20of%20mind%20were%20heading%20fearlessly%20into%20the%20realms%20of%20physics%20and%20astrophysics%2C%20of%20conducting%20experiments%20and%20making%20cool%20discoveries.%20Others%20like%20me%2C%20stood%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20vast%20skies%2C%20of%20realms%20far%20beyond%20our%20human%20imagination%2C%20and%20wondered%20why%20it%20felt%20so%20sacred.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20cycled%20home%2C%20my%20shirt%20billowing%20in%20the%20wind%2C%20wanting%20to%20urgently%20share%20everything%20with%20my%20sister%20who%20had%20missed%20it.%20Looking%20back%20at%20that%20singular%20evening%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20fortunate%20I%20was%20to%20have%20been%20shown%20the%20skies%20by%20such%20extraordinary%20visionaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20can%20introduce%20our%20children%20to%20something%20new%20in%20what%20appears%20ordinary%20and%20familiar%20and%20feed%20their%20delight%2C%20we%20set%20them%20and%20millions%20of%20Indians%20on%20a%20path%20of%20discovery%20that%20has%20no%20bounds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMihir%20Bhatt%20is%20director%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Disaster%20Mitigation%20Institute%2C%20Ahmedabad.%20He%20is%20currently%20working%20on%20space%20weather%20impact%20risks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693123567000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F27132543%2F8ed1c76b-d5ff-4ea4-8b57-b00075e01271.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Fa-childs-introduction-to-the-chandrayan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20friends%20and%20I%20stood%20wide-eyed%20around%20the%20balloon%2C%20trying%20not%20to%20get%20in%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20way%2C%20but%20too%20curious%20about%20the%20proceedings%20to%20actually%20stand%20aside.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fspace%2Fa-childs-introduction-to-the-chandrayan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Three%20US%20marines%20killed%20in%20Australia%20helicopter%20crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693123084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F83B3%2Fproduction%2F_115651733_breaking-large-promo-nc.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-66632201%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20more%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20hospital%20in%20a%20serious%20condition%2C%20US%20officials%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1251%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-66632201%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-66632201.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-australia-66632201.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Closing%20Down%20A%20City%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F08184234%2Fimage-2021-03-08T184223.035.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recently%20issued%20government%20notification%20for%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20a%20stunningly%20overpopulated%20city%20of%2032%2C941%2C000%20people%20%E2%80%93%20informs%20them%20that%20in%20view%20of%20the%20intense%20activities%20involving%20many%20VIPs%20during%20the%20three-day%20G20%20Summit%2C%20from%20September%208%20to%2010%2C%20the%20city%20must%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fwealth%2Fsave%2Fg20-summit-banks-to-remain-closed-in-delhi-on-these-dates%2Farticleshow%2F103061924.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ego%20into%20a%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fdelhi-schools-government-offices-to-remain-closed-from-september-8-10-for-g20-summit%2Farticleshow%2F102953989.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eclose%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20means%20all%20Delhi%20government%20and%20private%20offices%2C%20educational%20institutions%2C%20including%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%20will%20remain%20closed%20for%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district%2C%20furthermore%2C%20as%20per%20Section%2016(3)(i)%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Shops%20and%20Establishments%20Act%2C%201954%2C%20all%20banks%2C%20financial%20institutions%20and%20commercial%20establishments%20will%20also%20remain%20closed.%20A%20TV%20channel%2C%20ABP%20Live%2C%20portal%20said%20that%20not%20only%20Lutyens%20Delhi%2C%20but%20Old%20Delhi%20markets%20may%20also%20remain%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20this%2C%20major%20roads%20the%20VIPs%20will%20be%20using%20during%20the%20Summit%20will%20also%20be%20unavailable%20to%20citizens%E2%80%99%20vehicles%2C%20barring%20ambulances.%20The%20citizens%20are%20advised%20to%20stay%20indoors%20during%20the%20period%20to%20avoid%20congestion%20and%2For%20being%20penalised%20by%20traffic%20authorities%20if%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImportant%20questions%20from%20the%20traders%E2%80%99%20bodies%20have%20since%20been%20flowing%20out%3A%20all%20high-powered%20delegations%20arrive%20with%20VIP%20wives.%20Wives%20want%20to%20shop%20and%20visit%20exotic%20tourist%20spots%2C%20savour%20local%20food%20while%20their%20men%20discuss%20global%20affairs%20of%20war%2C%20peace%2C%20international%20trade%20and%20other%20such%20stuff.%20If%20this%20closing%20down%20plan%20is%20put%20into%20operation%2C%20how%20will%20they%20be%20able%20to%20do%20any%20of%20these%20things%20in%20our%20grand%20shopping%20malls%2C%20or%20Chandni%20Chowk%2C%20Karol%20Bagh%2C%20Khan%20Market%2C%20Sarojini%20Nagar%2C%20Kamala%20Nagar%20and%2For%20many%20other%20such%20places%3F%20Oh%2C%20the%20brains%20within%20the%20bureaucracy%20will%20doubtless%20do%20some%20%E2%80%9Cjugaad%E2%80%9D%20and%20see%20to%20it%20that%20the%20shoppers%20can%20shop%20and%20the%20others%20are%20stopped%20from%20crossing%20their%20paths%20to%20markets%2C%20Shanti%20Vana%2C%20National%20Museum%20et%20al.%20They%20always%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20the%20disastrous%20lockdown%20of%20a%20vast%20heart%20that%20an%20ancient%20city%20is%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20remember%20the%20sharp%20couplet%20of%20poet%20Jayasi%20about%20Khilji%20Sultan%E2%80%99s%20victory%20of%20Chittor%20that%20left%20silent%20mounds%20of%20bricks%20and%20ashes%20in%20a%20city%20of%20the%20dead.%20Way%20back%20in%201989%2C%20this%20writer%20had%20a%20taste%20of%20such%20desolation.%20A%20delegation%20of%20Indian%20writers%20U.R.%20Anant%20Murthy%2C%20Viren%20Bhattacharya%2C%20Gopichand%20Narang%20and%20myself%20landed%20in%20Beijing%20on%20June%204%20due%20to%20some%20diplomatic%20oversights.%20We%20were%20immediately%20driven%20in%20army%20vans%20to%20our%20hotel%20where%20we%20spent%20the%20next%20fortnight%20as%20privileged%20but%20locked%20up%20state%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20is%20history.%20There%20were%20no%20air%20raids%2C%20no%20%E2%80%98pacification%E2%80%99%20efforts%2C%20no%20bulldozing%20of%20public%20buildings%2C%20cemeteries%20or%20squares.%20But%20you%20sensed%20a%20vast%20fear%20hovering%20overhead%20like%20a%20vulture%20and%20slowly%20the%20revolt%20dying%20the%20way%20an%20oasis%20dies%2C%20when%20all%20natural%20wells%20and%20springs%20feeding%20it%20are%20stoppered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20on%20the%20mounds%20and%20ashes%20from%20that%20closing%20down%20by%20Deng%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20that%20the%20China%20of%20Xi%20has%20arisen%20powerful%2C%20confident%2C%20combative.%20A%20nation%20with%20vast%20ambitions%20radically%20distinct%20from%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20a%20writer%20of%20whatever%20stripe%2C%20at%20some%20point%20you%20are%20asked%20why%20at%20such%20moments%20you%20writers%20do%20not%20break%20through%20the%20cordon%20and%20go%20sit%20out%20there%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20crowds%3F%20The%20simplest%20and%20most%20honest%20answer%20is%2C%20because%20only%20a%20delusional%20writer%20works%20furiously%20through%20such%20times%20to%20produce%20what%20he%20or%20she%20expects%20to%20be%20radically%20transformative%20of%20a%20vast%20country%20without%20being%20close%20to%20its%20psychology%20or%20everyday%20life.%20Frankly%2C%20the%20people%20demanding%20radical%20socio-political%20change%2C%20demand%20not%20creative%20writing%20but%20manifestos%2C%20of%20their%20writers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2075%20years%20in%20Hindi%20literary%20circles%2C%20there%20have%20been%20na%C3%AFve%20attempts%20to%20connect%20the%20artists%E2%80%99%20work%20with%20the%20hard%20work%20put%20in%20by%20the%20truly%20labouring%20and%20grossly%20underpaid%20working%20classes.%20But%20to%20me%20the%20relationship%20then%20and%20even%20now%20between%20their%20demands%20and%20our%20capacity%20to%20write%2C%20remains%20somewhat%20tenuous.%20So%20writing%20quickies%20about%20the%20COVID-19%20years%20or%20the%20plight%20and%20pain%20of%20those%20that%20work%20and%20are%20paid%20daily%20by%20the%20clock%20when%20a%20city%20is%20closed%20down%20for%20foreign%20delegates%2C%20may%20be%20easy%20but%20inadvisable.%20That%20effort%20needs%20time%2C%20a%20vast%20canvas%20and%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20past%2075%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20see%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20that%20the%20vast%20working%20classes%20and%20craftsmen%20of%20India%20are%20affected%20very%20differently%20from%20those%20who%20create%20art%20objects%20for%20the%20delegates%20to%20buy%20or%20present%20a%20sanitized%20version%20of%20traditional%20Indian%20dancing%2C%20music%2C%20and%20drama%20while%20they%20are%20feasted%20upon%20in%20Hyderabad%20House%20or%20the%20mansions%20of%20the%20State.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20collective%20need%20Indians%20have%2C%20it%20is%20to%20assess%20the%20damage%20done%20to%20the%20labouring%20classes%20and%20small%20shopkeepers%20during%20the%20lockdown%2C%20it%20must%20be%20done%20separately%20from%20the%20ones%20that%20participated%20in%20the%20grand%20Summit%20as%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Face%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20two%20separate%20categories%20and%20must%20not%20be%20mixed%20together%20with%20those%20whose%20shanties%20are%20hidden%20behind%20vast%20plastic%20sheets%2C%20even%20though%20they%20have%20been%20beautifying%20the%20city%20and%20putting%20up%20art%20displays%20for%20the%20VIP%20visitors%20for%20months.%20They%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20have%20stencilled%20the%20age-old%20doctrine%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EVasudhaiv%20Kutumbakam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20the%20leadership%20will%20be%20verbally%20describing%20to%20the%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20middle-class%20writers%20will%20not%20greatly%20mind%20being%20cut%20off%20for%20three%20days.%20Their%20children%20take%20the%20break%20in%20their%20stride%20using%20the%20Internet%20to%20pass%20time%2C%20win%20friends%20and%20send%20out%20Instagram%20posts.%20The%20writers%20actually%20are%20quite%20used%20to%20being%20alone%2C%20and%20with%20extra%20time%20on%20their%20hands%2C%20thinking%20things%20through%20with%20clarity%20and%20grace%20enhanced.%20The%20heat%2C%20the%20confusion%2C%20fear%20and%20unrelenting%20tension%20of%20a%20country%20tragically%20divided%20by%20old%20and%20new%20fault%20lines%20hits%20the%20minorities%2C%20the%20labouring%20classes%20and%20daily%20wagers%20(often%20they%20are%20the%20one%20and%20the%20same)%20the%20hardest.%20Those%20who%20must%20live%20behind%20the%20plastic%20sheet%20and%20tarpaulin%20covered%20Bustees%20in%20the%20humid%20weather%2C%20their%20lanes%20choked%20with%20plastic%20and%20flammable%20waste%20and%20wandering%20cows.%20If%20someone%E2%80%99s%20wife%20goes%20into%20labour%2C%20or%20a%20child%20has%20lungs%20choked%20with%20phlegm%2C%20if%20there%20is%2C%20god%20forbid%2C%20a%20short%20circuit%20or%20a%20stove%20catches%20fire%20in%20some%20drunk%E2%80%99s%20kitchen%2C%20or%20the%20cow%20vigilantes%20come%20threatening%2C%20who%20do%20they%20call%3F%20Where%20do%20they%20go%20%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForget%20Delhi%2C%20where%20did%20the%20people%20in%20Nuh%20go%3F%20Or%20in%20Manipur%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20ex-bureaucrat%20on%20TV%20was%20known%20to%20be%20an%20upright%20worker%20and%20a%20stickler%20for%20rules%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20saddle.%20He%20has%20since%20greyed%20but%20been%20re-employed%20in%20a%20very%20different%20capacity%20for%20a%20very%20important%20project%20slated%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20early%20next%20year.%20The%20chair%20he%20sits%20in%20is%20a%20magnificent%20burnished%20throne.%20The%20wall%20of%20books%20behind%20him%20has%20the%20usual%20Gandhian%20Charkha%20and%20Ganesha%20and%20sundry%20holy%20statues.%20As%20a%20journalist%2C%20one%20admired%20his%20handling%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20modernisation%20very%20efficiently%20across%20the%20states.%20He%20was%20then%20gruff%2C%20unapproachable%2C%20and%20like%20most%20Delhi%20bureaucrats%20of%20his%20vintage%2C%20dismissive%20of%20Hindi%20journalists.%20Today%20he%20has%20a%20caste%20mark%2C%20a%20holy%20ritual%20thread%20on%20his%20wrist%20and%20a%20ring%20with%20a%20large%20stone%20on%20his%20pinkie.%20He%20is%20speaking%20about%20%E2%80%98The%20Project%E2%80%99%20in%20flawless%20Hindi%20to%20his%20interlocutor%20and%20smiles%20like%20a%20benign%20saint.%20Things%20are%20going%20smoothly%2C%20he%20says.%20God%20willing%2C%20the%20project%20will%20be%20ready%20on%20time.%20Would%20the%20delegates%20be%20visiting%20his%20site%20%3F%20He%20says%20he%20does%20not%20know%20and%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20sheer%20habit%2C%20one%20feels%20like%20asking%20him%20details.%20How%3F%20What%20does%20divine%20intervention%20have%20to%20do%20with%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20project%3F%20Is%20he%20sure%20God%20will%20oblige%3F%20But%20such%20questions%20will%20go%20unanswered%20or%20else%20he%20will%20come%20up%20with%20some%20fables%20and%20quotes%20on%20leadership%20likely%20to%20diminish%20both%20him%20and%20the%20anchor.%20You%20switch%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693122089000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F08184234%2Fimage-2021-03-08T184223.035.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-g20-summit-closing-down-a-city%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20G20%20summit%20approaches%2C%20the%20closure%20of%20Delhi's%20government%20and%20private%20offices%2C%20educational%20institutions%2C%20banks%2C%20and%20commercial%20establishments%20for%20three%20days%20raises%20concerns%2C%20particularly%20among%20traders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-g20-summit-closing-down-a-city%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dawn%20of%20revolution%20lit%20up%20dark%20side%20of%20moon%3A%20PM%20Modi%20on%20'Mann%20Ki%20Baat'%22%2C%22co