20type%20these%20words%2C%20the%20chess%20career%20of%20Rameshbabu%20%E2%80%9CPragg%E2%80%9D%20Praggnanandhaa%20resembles%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20first%20act%20of%20a%20biopic%20about%20a%20child%20prodigy%20destined%20for%20greatness%20and%20his%20place%20amongst%20the%20geniuses%20of%20history.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHighlights%20of%20this%20time%20are%20known%20to%20all%20those%20who%20have%20not%20been%20living%20under%20a%20rock%20the%20past%20decade%20and%20especially%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20From%20learning%20the%20game%20at%203%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20International%20Master%20of%20all%20time%20(since%20beaten)%2C%20becoming%20the%20second-youngest%20grandmaster%20of%20all%20time%20(since%20broken)%2C%20the%20youngest-ever%20to%20cross%20the%202600%20FIDE%20rating-barrier%20and%20many%2C%20many%20other%20achievements%2C%20rival%20the%20legendary%20feats%20of%20legends%20and%20biopic%20icons%20like%20Tendulkar%2C%20Federer%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9CMozart%20of%20Chess%E2%80%9D%2C%20best%20player%20of%20all%20time%20by%20universal%20opinion%2C%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20himself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFramed%20within%20this%20narrative%2C%20the%20FIDE%20World%20Cup%202023%20held%20in%20Baku%2C%20Azerbaijan%2C%20became%20the%20battleground%20of%20two%20mutually%20opposing%20biopics-in-the-making%20over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20month%20of%20enthralling%2C%20exciting%2C%20almost-scripted%20chess.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20the%20greatest%20player%20of%20all%20time%2C%20Carlsen%2C%20chasing%20the%20only%20trophy%20still%20missing%20from%20his%20GOAT%20cabinet%20comprising%20five%20Classical%2C%20four%20Rapid%20and%20six%20Blitz%20World-Championships.%20Pragg%2C%20the%20David%20to%20this%20Goliath%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20entered%20the%20tournament%20having%20never%20lost%20to%20Carlsen%20in%20the%20Classical%20time-format%20and%20beaten%20him%20in%20a%20series%20of%20history-making%20Rapid%20and%20Blitz%20encounters%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20player%20ever%20to%20beat%20Carlsen%20in%20the%20process.%20However%2C%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20his%20journey%20was%20devoid%20of%20the%20minor%20conflicts%20fuelling%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Pragg%2C%20trailblazer%20of%20the%20path%20his%20fellow%20child%20prodigies%20grandmasters%20Nihal%20Sarin%2C%20Arjun%20Erigaisi%2C%20and%20D.%20Gukesh%20have%20followed%2C%20had%20lagged%20slightly%20behind%20in%20FIDE%20ratings%20which%20determine%20global%20chess%20rankings%20compared%20to%20his%20peers.%20Pragg%20entered%20the%20tournament%20at%202690%20rating%20points%2C%20perilously%20close%20to%20breaking%20the%202700%20barrier%20%E2%80%93%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20double-century%20to%20a%20century%20in%20Grandmaster%20Chess%20%E2%80%93%20which%20awards%20the%20player%20the%20unofficial%20moniker%20of%20a%20Super-GM.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Gukesh%20and%20Erigaisi%20have%20already%20breached%20this%20barrier%20and%20made%20their%20ways%20into%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Top-20%20players%2C%20while%20Gukesh%2C%20the%20youngest%20of%20the%20prodigies%2C%20has%20already%20stormed%20into%20the%20top-10%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20surpass%20Viswanathan%20Anand%20in%20close%20to%20four-decades.%20To%20top%20it%20all%2C%20all%20four%20prodigies%20are%20classmates%20at%20the%20WestBridge-Anand%20Chess%20Academy%2C%20set%20up%20on%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Chess%20Schools%20of%20legend%20for%20nurturing%20chess%20talent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20cusp%20of%20turning%20into%20an%20adult%2C%20Pragg%20entered%20the%20tournament%20with%20the%20scene%20set%20for%20a%20great%20coming-of-age%20climax%2C%20seeded%2031st.%20The%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20proceeded%20in%20Baku%20as%20if%20it%20were%20written.%20A%20bye%20in%20the%20first%20round%20and%20victories%20over%20grandmasters%20Maxime%20Lagarde%20and%20David%20Navarra%20in%20the%20round%20of%2016%20went%20unremarkably%20well%2C%20like%20matches%20shown%20briefly%20with%20the%20results%2C%201.5-0.5%20in%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%20favour%2C%20written%20over%20a%20scene.%20The%20highlight%20came%20on%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%2018th%20birthday%2C%20his%20initiation%20as%20an%20adult%20voting-citizen%20of%20India.%20It%20was%20akin%20to%20a%20chess%20equivalent%20of%20an%20initiation%20ritual%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20King%20Leonidas%E2%80%99%20slaying%20of%20the%20wolf%20in%20Zack%20Snyder%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E300%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0or%20Hercules%E2%80%99%20slaying%20of%20the%20Nemean%20Lion%20in%20Greek%20mythology.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPragg%20faced%20grandmaster%20Hikaru%20Nakamura%2C%20ranked%20second%20in%20the%20world%20and%20in%20the%20best%20form%20of%20his%20life%20over%20the%20past%20year%20since%202022%2C%20on%20his%2018th%20birthday%2C%20securing%20a%20draw%20in%20a%20Classical%20game%2C%20forcing%20tie-breaks%20the%20following%20day%20in%20Rapid%20and%20Blitz.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20he%20stunningly%20beat%20Nakamura%20%E2%80%93%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9CSpeed-Demon%E2%80%9D%20of%20Chess%20for%20his%20mastery%20in%20faster%20time-controls%20%E2%80%93%20in%20two%20consecutive%20games%2C%20knocking%20him%20out%20of%20the%20tournament.%20Magnus%20Carlsen%2C%20playing%20his%20own%20game%20after%20having%20narrowly%20escaped%20elimination%20by%20a%20child%20prodigy%20himself%20in%20an%20earlier%20round%2C%20got%20up%20from%20his%20ongoing%20game%20to%20congratulate%20Pragg%20upon%20the%20result%20%E2%80%93%20a%20gesture%20almost%20unheard-of%20in%20tournament%20chess.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20in%20an%20interview%20what%20he%20told%20the%20Indian%2C%20Carlsen%20repeated%20the%20mantra%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%20coach%20grandmaster%20R.B.%20Ramesh%20has%20been%20telling%20anyone%20who%20will%20listen%20at%20Carlsen%E2%80%99s%20Norwegian%20camp%20for%20chess%E2%80%99s%20wunderkinds%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20told%20him%20today%20we%20all%20want%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20like%20Pragg%E2%80%9D.%20A%20smooth%20victory%20over%20grandmaster%20Ferenc%20Berkes%20followed%20in%20the%20fifth%20round%20before%20the%20drama%20shifted%20to%20internal%20conflicts%3A%20in%20the%20quarter-finals%2C%20Pragg%20was%20to%20play%20%E2%80%9Cbest-friend%E2%80%9D%2C%20classmate%2C%20and%20compatriot%20grandmaster%20Arjun%20Erigaisi.%20The%20winner%20would%20effectively%20seal%20his%20spot%20in%20the%20Candidates%20Tournament%20to%20decide%20a%20challenger%20for%20the%20World%20Chess%20Championship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20match%20both%20players%20confessed%20to%20spending%20their%20time%20between%20matches%20hanging%20out%20with%20each%20other%2C%20discussing%20chess%2C%20and%20playing%20TT.%20They%20professed%20to%20doing%20the%20same%20on%20the%20rest%20day%20before%20their%20match%20as%20well%2C%20discussing%20everything%20except%20chess%2C%20but%20when%20the%20pieces%20aligned%20and%20the%20clock%20struck%2C%20all%20bets%20were%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArjun%20got%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20first%20Classical%20match%2C%20forcing%20Pragg%20to%20win%20on%20demand%20in%20the%20second%20Classical%20game%20the%20following%20day.%20He%20did%2C%20forcing%20tie-breaks%20which%20was%20some%20of%20the%20most%20up-and-down%20emotionally%20nerve-wracking%20chess-watching%20experience%20ever%20produced%20at%20the%20World%20Cup.%20It%20took%20nine%20games%20across%2025%20minutes%2C%2010%20minutes%2C%20and%20finally%205%20minutes%20per%20side%20where%20both%20friends%20traded%20blow-for-blow%2C%20both%20beating%20each%20other%20on%20demand%20to%20keep%20the%20match%20going%20until%20Pragg%20scored%20the%20final%20victory%2C%20finishing%20half-a-point%20ahead%2C%20through%20to%20the%20semis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20Indians%20entered%20the%20last%20eight%20of%20the%20tournament%20%E2%80%93%20the%20best%20by%20far%20India%20has%20ever%20done%2C%20the%20dawn%20of%20a%20new%20%E2%80%9Cera%20of%20youngsters%E2%80%9D%20in%20Ramesh%E2%80%99s%20words.%20When%20the%20semis%20began%2C%20Pragg%20was%20the%20lone%20survivor%2C%20the%20only%20Indian%20since%20Anand%20to%20make%20it%20this%20far.%20His%20opponent%2C%20ranked%20third%20in%20the%20world%2C%20grandmaster%20Fabiano%20Caruana%20%E2%80%93%20a%20former%20World-Championship%20challenger%20to%20Magnus%20himself.%20The%20match%20proceeded%20as%20their%20ratings%20would%20suggest%2C%20with%20Fabiano%20bearing%20down%20on%20Pragg%2C%20pushing%20his%20position%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20defeat%20in%20both%20Classical%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Pragg%20showed%20extraordinary%20resilience%20and%20nerve%20to%20keep%20finding%20defensive%20resources%20in%20a%20worse%20position%2C%20suffering%20for%20hours%20on%20both%20days%20in%20order%20to%20deny%20Caruana%20the%20win.%20Legends%20marveled%20at%20the%20teenager%E2%80%99s%20resiliency%2C%20and%20the%20ongoing%20come-of-age%20of%20a%20boy-wonder%20they%20were%20all%20witnessing%20on%20the%20board.%20The%20same%20pattern%20largely%20followed%20in%20shorter%20time-controls%20in%20tie-breaks%2C%20with%20Caruana%20pressing%20and%20Pragg%20forced%20to%20defend%2C%20which%20he%20did%20remarkably%20creatively%20and%20doggedly.%20The%20narrative%20flipped%20for%20just%20one%20game%20where%20Pragg%20managed%20to%20get%20an%20advantage%20with%20White%2C%20and%20he%20went%20on%20to%20convert%20his%20advantage%20the%20only%20time%20he%20got%20it%20in%20the%20match%2C%20knocking%20out%20another%20giant%20of%20the%20game.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20became%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20ever%20make%20it%20to%20the%20finals%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20process.%20He%20also%20qualified%20for%20the%20Candidates%20Tournament%20%E2%80%93%20the%20only%20one%20since%20Anand%2C%20and%20the%20third-youngest%20ever%20behind%20two%20of%20the%20games%E2%80%99%20greatest%3A%20Bobby%20Fischer%20and%20Carlsen%20himself%2C%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%20opponent%20in%20the%20final.%20He%E2%80%99d%20also%20crossed%20the%202700%20rating%20barrier%20by%20some%20distance%2C%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20World%20top-20%2C%20the%20lowest-seed%20ever%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20at%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Everything%20was%20set%20for%20the%20ultimate%20David%20versus%20Goliath%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEverything%20except%20Carlsen%E2%80%99s%20own%20story%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%20The%20Norwegian%2C%20who%20is%20synonymous%20in%20chess%20with%20the%20GOAT%20in%20a%20sport%20where%20other%20players%20are%20called%20demons%20and%20monsters%2C%20had%20already%20knocked%20out%20Gukesh%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20final%2C%20determined%20to%20win%20it%20as%20the%20missing%20feather%20in%20his%20bejeweled%20cap.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Carlsen%E2%80%99s%20will%2C%20as%20it%20often%20does%2C%20dictated%20the%20result.%20Despite%20Carlsen%20battling%20a%20stomach%20bug%20and%20Pragg%20drawing%20both%20Classical%20games%20to%20remain%20unbeaten%20against%20Carlsen%20in%20this%20format%2C%20Carlsen%20broke%20through%20with%20a%20win%20in%20the%20first%20game%20of%20the%20tiebreak%2C%20drawing%20the%20second%20game%20to%20finish%20half-a-point%20ahead%20as%20the%20winner%20of%20the%202023%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20end-result%2C%20this%20performance%20in%20the%20first-arc%20has%20determined%20the%20trajectory%20a%20nation%20of%20experts%20and%20fans%20alike%20expects%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20story.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%20Anand%2C%20an%20Indian%20is%20in%20the%20candidates%2C%20only%2018%20years%20old%2C%20and%20material%20for%20a%20montage%20of%20a%20nation%20proud%20and%20legends%20fawning%20can%20be%20found%20on%20virtually%20any%20news%20platform.%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20to%20Anand%20Mahindra%20%E2%80%93%20adulation%20has%20poured%20in%20from%20all%20directions.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Pragg%20wins%20around%20the%20time%20Chandrayaan%20lands%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20be%20too%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishwanathan%20Anand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fif-r-praggnanandhaa-wins-world-cup-around-the-time-chandrayaan-lands-viswanathan-anand-to-ndtv-4319102%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3ENDTV%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20evoking%20a%20nostalgia%20of%20the%20space-race%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20Bobby%20Fischer%20during%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20expectational%20narratives%20for%20Pragg%20are%20nested%20in%20the%20explosive%20narrative%20of%20the%20growth%20of%20chess%20and%20its%20budding%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20generation%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%2C%20well%20on%20its%20way%20to%20be%20the%20next%20dominant%20chess-power%20in%20the%20world%2C%20gifted%20with%20the%20best%20Junior%20(under%2020%20years)%20players%20in%20the%20world%20being%20mentored%20by%20former%20world%20champions%20like%20Vladimir%20Kramnik%2C%20Boris%20Gelfand%2C%20Magnus%20Carlsen%20and%20Anand%20himself%2C%20besides%20their%20personal%20coaches%20like%20Ramesh%20who%20are%20amongst%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20as%20training%20staff.%20Performances%20like%20Pragg%E2%80%99s%20and%20Gukesh%E2%80%99s%20have%20inspired%20thousands%2C%20especially%20children%2C%20and%20brought%20eye-balls%20to%20chess%20on%20a%20whole%20new%20level%2C%20leading%20to%20sponsorships%20and%20increased%20access%20for%20more%20to%20play%20the%20sport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20safe%20to%20say%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20is%20set%20for%20the%20second-act%E2%80%99s%20commencement.%20For%20his%20part%2C%20Pragg%20is%20already%20off%20to%20play%20in%20his%20next%20tournament.%20A%20milestone%20has%20been%20set%20at%20the%20Candidates%20Tournament%2C%20and%20Pragg%20admits%20of%20his%20ambition%20to%20be%20world%20champion%20as%20his%20long-term%20goal%20in%20chess.%20This%20tournament%20requires%20training%20in%20a%20way%20no%20other%20tournament%20does%20in%20chess%2C%20and%20Pragg%20has%20booked%20his%20seat%20quite%20in%20advance.%20Cue%20the%20training%20montage%20%E2%80%93%20all%20of%20India%20better%20watch%20out%20for%20this%20sporting%20story!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbpriyaranjan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBinit%20Priyaranjan%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20masters%20in%20philosophy%20from%20St.%20Stephens%20College%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693113432000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F22134142%2FR-Praggnanandhaa.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fpraggnanandhaas-remarkable-first-act-sets-the-stage-for-an-epic-journey-in-the-chess-world%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20outcome%2C%20this%20performance%20in%20the%20first%20arc%20has%20set%20the%20expectations%20of%20both%20experts%20and%20fans%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20story's%20trajectory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fpraggnanandhaas-remarkable-first-act-sets-the-stage-for-an-epic-journey-in-the-chess-world%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Papier%20Mache%20Artisans%20Struggle%20to%20Preserve%20and%20Conserve%20Their%20Indigenous%20Craft%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26193637%2FKPM1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20part%20three%20of%20a%20three-part%20series%20undertaken%20by%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvisualstoryboardscnes.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EVisual%20Storyboard%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20initiative%20of%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20Read%20part%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fpapier-mache-kashmir-art-dying%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20part%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkashmir-papier-mache-craft-wane-authenticity%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVisual%20Storyboards%E2%80%99%20work%20can%20be%20accessed%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvisualstoryboardscnes.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20For%20this%20project%2C%20please%20find%20all%20video%20essays%20published%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPL8RbNXSvnr8QZ9EhRXib4M7c1l1FYMBM-%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20artists%20in%20states%20across%20India%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20future%20and%20the%20preservation%20of%20traditional%20handicrafts%20as%20they%20witness%20a%20decline%20in%20interest%20among%20the%20younger%20generation%20to%20take%20over%20the%20process%20of%20work%20in%20producing%20these%20while%20maintaining%20the%20authenticity%20and%20purity%20of%20the%20craft%E2%80%99s%20indigenous%20production%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20modernisation%20and%20globalisation%20have%20taken%20centre%20stage%2C%20traditional%20crafts%20have%20experienced%20a%20loss%20of%20prestige%20and%20financial%20viability.%20Young%20people%2C%20influenced%20by%20changing%20societal%20norms%20and%20career%20opportunities%2C%20are%20increasingly%20choosing%20to%20pursue%20other%20professions%20that%20offer%20higher%20earning%20potential%20and%20greater%20social%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shift%20in%20career%20choices%20poses%20a%20significant%20threat%20to%20the%20survival%20of%20traditional%20crafts%2C%20as%20the%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20passed%20down%20through%20generations%20could%20be%20lost%20forever.%20To%20counter%20this%20trend%20and%20secure%20a%20future%20for%20their%20craft%2C%20many%20artisans%20have%20taken%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20initiate%20various%20programs%20and%20initiatives%20aimed%20at%20engaging%20and%20inspiring%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmed%20Khan%2C%20an%20experienced%20exporter%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Epapier%20mache%3C%2Fem%3E%20products%2C%20expands%20on%20this%20problem%20by%20discussing%20how%20the%20state%20does%20little%20to%20provide%20better%20access%20to%20domestic%20and%20cross-border%20markets%20for%20such%20unique%20products%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20give%20you%20an%20example%20of%20our%20difficulties%2C%20a%20shipment%20of%20ours%20has%20been%20stuck%20at%20the%20borders%20of%20the%20Netherlands%20for%20the%20past%20week.%20The%20officials%20there%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20VAX%20number%2C%20which%20I%20applied%20for%20a%20month%20ago.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20help%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20end%20to%20help%2C%20instead%2C%20I%20have%20been%20making%20rounds%20to%20their%20offices%20in%20vain.%20Usually%2C%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20take%2010%20days%20to%20arrive%2C%20and%20currently%2C%20despite%20the%20delay%2C%20we%20are%20not%20being%20offered%20any%20updates.%20Now%2C%20it%20would%E2%80%99ve%20been%20different%20if%20this%20shipment%20were%20just%20about%20me%20and%20my%20needs%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not.%20I%20have%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20artists%20working%20under%20me%20whose%20households%20depend%20on%20the%20payment%20from%20this%20order.%20How%20am%20I%20supposed%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20money%20when%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20it%20myself%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20last%20generation%20of%20p%3Cem%3Eapier%20mache%3C%2Fem%3E%20artists%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exploitative%20nature%20of%20the%20relationship%20with%20exporters%20and%20the%20rising%20cost%20prices%20of%20the%20products%20gives%20more%20reasons%20for%20the%20younger%20generation%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20age-old%20tradition%20of%20papier%20mache%20art.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20these%20vulnerabilities%2C%20there%20is%20a%20rising%20shortage%20of%20expertise%20as%20there%20are%20very%20few%20people%20with%20indigenous%20knowledge%20of%20the%20art%20remaining%20in%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Saad*%20explains%20in%20detail%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20the%20demand%20for%20papier%20mache%20products%20has%20remained%20consistent%2C%20the%20supply%20has%20drastically%20reduced%20due%20to%20the%20dwindling%20number%20of%20artisans.%20While%20the%20prices%20of%20these%20products%20have%20not%20increased%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20raw%20materials%20has%20risen.%20Consequently%2C%20although%20papier%20mache%20products%20command%20a%20high%20price%20in%20the%20market%2C%20the%20artists%20themselves%20are%20unable%20to%20meet%20their%20basic%20needs.%20Many%20artisans%20have%20been%20compelled%20to%20switch%20to%20other%20professions%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F2tYXRlKZRZI%3Fsi%3DIGE9mVsjJ3dSZBeP%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20isolation%20endured%20by%20this%20community%20of%20artisans%20not%20only%20affects%20their%20social%20interactions%20but%20also%20has%20an%20impact%20on%20their%20overall%20health%20and%20well-being.%20As%20the%20low%20earning%20potential%20associated%20with%20this%20craft%20serves%20as%20a%20major%20deterrent%20for%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%20the%20artisans%20continue%20to%20yearn%20for%20a%20more%20lucrative%20solution%20to%20their%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20issue%20that%20affects%20craftsmen%20and%20artisans%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20restrictions%20faced%20by%20them%20in%20accessing%20a%20direct%20marketplace%20for%20their%20work%2C%20mediated%20by%20a%20standard%20benchmarking%20process%20which%20embraces%20the%20authentic%20craft%20over%20those%20that%20imitate%20or%20counterfeit%20its%20production%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20the%20artists%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20%E2%80%98intermediaries%E2%80%99%20to%20facilitate%20selling%20of%20such%20products.%20This%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20had%20the%20effect%20of%20a%20reduced%20level%20of%20autonomy%20in%20the%20production%20process%20for%20the%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvaiz%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20adapt%20to%20market%20trends%2C%20I%20introduced%20drawing%20papier%20machie%20designs%20on%20iron%2C%20glass%2C%20and%20stainless%20steel%20products.%20Artisans%20working%20on%20these%20new%20materials%20are%20able%20to%20earn%20a%20satisfactory%20income%2C%20while%20those%20who%20remain%20dedicated%20to%20the%20original%20papier%20machie%20work%20are%20often%20dissatisfied.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20tighter%20timelines%20and%20producing%20bulk%20orders%20for%20the%20international%20market%20means%20that%20artists%20who%20can%20deliver%20on%20such%20schedules%20have%20to%20sacrifice%20quality%20in%20favor%20of%20quantity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20designs%20of%20the%20artworks%20are%20now%20dictated%20as%20per%20the%20customer%20preferences%2C%20who%20reside%20in%20international%20markets%20such%20as%20Europe%2C%20shifting%20the%20products%20from%20an%20expression%20of%20their%20cultural%20identity%20to%20ornaments%20meant%20for%20traditional%20Christian%20festivals%20like%20Christmas.%20While%20such%20orders%20are%20useful%20for%20sustaining%20their%20lives%2C%20artists%20rues%20that%20such%20changes%20have%20reduced%20the%20agency%20of%20the%20artists%20from%20their%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F2tYXRlKZRZI%3Fsi%3DV3leud4O98K13lNu%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20detrimental%20effects%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20cultural%20capital%20in%20a%20rich%20kaleidoscopic%20knowledge%20and%20handicrafts%20capital%20of%20Kashmir%20are%20profound%20and%20far-reaching.%20Rapid%20commercialization%20and%20mechanization%20of%20traditional%20art%20forms%20have%20led%20to%20a%20decline%20in%20authenticity%20and%20cultural%20identity.%20As%20machines%20take%20over%20the%20production%20process%2C%20artisans%20lose%20their%20bargaining%20power%2C%20resulting%20in%20reduced%20compensations%20and%20limited%20training%20opportunities%20for%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20erosion%20of%20cultural%20knowledge%20and%20expertise%20has%20weakened%20artistic%20skills%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20unique%20cultural%20heritage.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20decline%20of%20traditional%20art%20forms%20has%20had%20severe%20economic%20consequences%20for%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20artisans%20and%20communities%20dependent%20on%20these%20crafts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20decline%20of%20cultural%20tourism%20and%20educational%20impact%20further%20accentuate%20the%20need%20to%20preserve%20and%20revitalise%20traditional%20art%20forms.%20To%20safeguard%20India%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20capital%2C%20concerted%20efforts%20are%20necessary%20to%20recognise%2C%20support%20and%20promote%20these%20invaluable%20art%20forms%2C%20ensuring%20they%20continue%20to%20enrich%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20fabric%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26193646%2FKMP2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26193646%2FKMP2.png%20936w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26193646%2FKMP2-300x169.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20preserving%20the%20crafts%2C%20papier%20mache%20artists%20are%20making%20efforts%20to%20teach%20the%20young%20about%20the%20craft%E2%80%99s%20rich%20indigenous%20and%20cultural%20history%20which%20instills%20a%20sense%20of%20pride%20and%20appreciation%20for%20their%20craft%20among%20young%20people%20-learning%20the%20work.%20They%20organise%20workshops%2C%20training%20sessions%2C%20and%20interactive%20events%20to%20showcase%20the%20beauty%20and%20significance%20of%20traditional%20crafts.%20%C2%A0Educational%20institutions%20can%20do%20more%20to%20promote%20these%20in%20partnership%20with%20papier%20mache%20handicraft%20workshop%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20hands-on%20experiences%20and%20sharing%20stories%20about%20the%20cultural%20heritage%20behind%20each%20craft%2C%20they%20hope%20to%20reignite%20interest%20and%20curiosity%20among%20the%20youth.%20In%20addition%20to%20educational%20efforts%2C%20some%20artists%20are%20also%20exploring%20ways%20to%20make%20traditional%20crafts%20more%20relevant%20to%20contemporary%20tastes%20and%20demands.%20They%20are%20experimenting%20with%20modern%20designs%2C%20incorporating%20sustainable%20practices%2C%20and%20utilizing%20innovative%20marketing%20strategies%20to%20attract%20a%20wider%20audience%2C%20including%20the%20younger%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20artists%E2%80%99%20commendable%20efforts%2C%20one%20major%20hindrance%20in%20their%20mission%20to%20preserve%20traditional%20crafts%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20significant%20support%20from%20the%20government.%20While%20some%20local%20and%20regional%20authorities%20may%20show%20interest%20and%20offer%20limited%20backing%2C%20a%20cohesive%20and%20nation-wide%20approach%20is%20lacking.%20Without%20substantial%20government%20support%2C%20it%20becomes%20challenging%20to%20scale%20up%20these%20initiatives%2C%20reach%20a%20larger%20audience%2C%20and%20provide%20better%20infrastructure%20for%20skill%20development%20and%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20is%20crucial%20in%20creating%20an%20ecosystem%20that%20fosters%20the%20preservation%20and%20promotion%20of%20traditional%20crafts.%20Financial%20assistance%2C%20policy%20incentives%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20development%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20encouraging%20young%20people%20to%20pursue%20careers%20in%20traditional%20crafts.%20Furthermore%2C%20incorporating%20traditional%20crafts%20into%20educational%20curricula%20can%20help%20raise%20awareness%20and%20appreciation%20among%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENames%20of%20all%20respondents%20have%20been%20changed%20to%20protect%20their%20identity%20and%20maintain%20anonymity.%20The%20authors%20would%20like%20to%20especially%20thank%20Dr.%20Rekha%20Pachauri%20and%20Dr.%20Meera%20Shirodkar%20for%20their%20assistance%20with%20field%20work%2C%20interviews%20and%20in%20the%20audio-video%20documentation%20of%20the%20study.%20Without%20their%20support%2C%20this%20study%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible.%20All%20photographs%20are%20credited%20to%20them%20and%20Ishfaq%20Ahmad%20Wani.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20(CNES)%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20Ishfaq%20Ahmad%20Wani%20is%20a%20Contributing%20Research%20Analyst%20with%20CNES%20Visual%20Storyboards.%20Tavleen%20Kaur%20and%20Hima%20Trisha%20are%20Senior%20Research%20Analysts%20and%20CNES%20Visual%20Storyboards%20team%20leads.%20Yashovardhan%20Chaturvedi%20and%20Anousha%20Singh%20are%20Research%20Analysts%20with%20CNES.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693110650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26193637%2FKPM1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fhow-papier-mache-artisans-struggle-to-preserve-and-conserve-their-indigenous-craft%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20modernisation%20and%20globalisation%20have%20taken%20centre%20stage%2C%20traditional%20crafts%20have%20experienced%20a%20loss%20of%20prestige%20and%20financial%20viability.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fhow-papier-mache-artisans-struggle-to-preserve-and-conserve-their-indigenous-craft%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Is%20in%20the%20Dark%2C%20the%20Ban%20on%20the%20Internet%20Must%20Be%20Lifted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170310%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-26-at-4.34.21-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20over%20a%20hundred%20days%20since%20the%20government%20of%20Manipur%20decided%20to%20ban%20internet%20access%20across%20the%20state.%20It%20is%20now%20more%20important%20than%20ever%20to%20understand%20that%20the%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20ostensibly%20ordered%20to%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20has%20done%20little%20to%20prevent%20violence%20or%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20making%20people%20safer%2C%20the%20shutdown%20violates%20their%20rights%20and%20has%20had%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20their%20lives.%20It%20has%20resulted%20in%20communities%20being%20unable%20to%20receive%20and%20impart%20informed%20and%20verified%20information%20about%20their%20families%E2%80%99%20well-being%20and%20safety%2C%20it%20has%20denied%20citizens%20their%20right%20to%20peacefully%20dissent%20against%20the%20government%2C%20and%20has%20resulted%20in%20journalists%20facing%20challenges%20while%20reporting%20on%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20other%2C%20more%20serious%20instances%2C%20the%20shutdown%20prevented%20people%20from%20hearing%20about%20cases%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Finternet-shutdown-manipur-burning-in-the-dark%2F%5C%22%3Ebrutal%20murder%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sexual%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20subsequent%20orders%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finternetfreedom.in%2Fmanipur-100-days-internet-shutdown%2F%5C%22%3Epartially%20lifted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20shutdown%E2%80%99s%20restrictions%20had%20little%20impact%20because%20the%20lift%20only%20targeted%20broadband%20internet%20connections.%20This%20argument%20is%20especially%20compelling%20when%20one%20considers%20that%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20users%20in%20the%20country%2C%2096%25%20to%20be%20specific%2C%20rely%20on%20mobile%20data%20connections%20to%20access%20the%20internet.%20This%20figure%20is%20based%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20data%2C%20and%20was%20highlighted%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Freport%2F2023%2F06%2F14%2Fno-internet-means-no-work-no-pay-no-food%2Finternet-shutdowns-deny-access-basic%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20titled%20%E2%80%9CNo%20Internet%20Means%20No%20Work%2C%20No%20Pay%2C%20No%20Food%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20was%20co-published%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20negative%20impact%20the%20shutdown%20has%20had%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20one%20has%20to%20wonder%20why%20it%20is%20still%20being%20enforced.%20Why%20would%20the%20government%20employ%20a%20method%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D3330413%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20to%20be%20ineffective%20at%20reducing%20violence%2C%20even%20after%20a%20hundred%20days%3F%20Unfortunately%2C%20one%20answer%20is%20that%20shutdowns%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20in%20Manipur%2C%20serve%20only%20the%20interests%20of%20autocratic%20governments%20which%20seek%20to%20impose%20an%20information%20blackout.%20For%20months%2C%20this%20blackout%20has%20shielded%20gross%20human%20rights%20violations%20and%20served%20to%20save%20the%20face%20of%20a%20government%20that%20has%20been%20inept%20in%20dealing%20with%20what%20is%20possibly%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20worst%20human%20rights%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20publication%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcentre-works-on-aid-packages-for-manipurs-displaced-in-camps-farmers-8875527%2F%5C%22%3E56%2C000%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes%20by%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20were%20seeking%20refuge%20in%20relief%20camps.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmizoram-to-disburse-humanitarian-aid-to-the-displaced-this-week%2Farticleshow%2F102881261.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20government%20of%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%2C%2013%2C000%20internally%20displaced%20people%20(IDPs)%20have%20sought%20refuge%20in%20their%20state.%20Relief%20camps%20established%20to%20house%20displaced%20communities%20continue%20to%20require%20immediate%20attention%2C%20including%20medical%20and%20sanitation%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20situations%20like%20this%2C%20it%20is%20natural%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20shutdown%20will%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20displaced%20communities%E2%80%99%20ability%20to%20access%20the%20internet.%20The%20shutdown%20prevents%20us%20from%20fully%20understanding%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20human%20rights%20crisis%2C%20and%20it%20is%20therefore%20critical%20that%20the%20government%20end%20it.%20The%20government%20can%20no%20longer%20use%20excuses%20to%20continue%20enforcing%20the%20state%20shutdown.%20Instead%2C%20it%20must%20make%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20work%20together%20with%20civil%20society%20in%20order%20to%20implement%20other%20approaches%20that%20effectively%20address%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20challenges%20without%20resorting%20to%20one%20that%20restricts%20human%20rights.%20If%20it%20is%20unable%20to%20fulfil%20this%20basic%20duty%2C%20the%20government%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20while%20the%20rights%20of%20millions%20of%20its%20citizens%20are%20violated%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJade%20Lyngdoh%20is%20a%20lawyer%20and%20writer%20based%20in%20Shillong%2C%20Meghalaya.%20He%20was%20a%20Meta%20India%20Tech%20Scholar%20(2021-22)%20at%20the%20National%20Law%20University%20in%20Jodhpur%2C%20where%20he%20studied%20constitutional%20law.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693107054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26170310%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-26-at-4.34.21-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-is-in-the-dark-the-ban-on-the-internet-must-be-lifted%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Subsequent%20orders%20that%20partially%20lifted%20the%20shutdown's%20restrictions%20had%20little%20impact%20because%20the%20lift%20only%20targeted%20broadband%20internet%20connections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-is-in-the-dark-the-ban-on-the-internet-must-be-lifted%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mnangagwa%20re-elected%20president%20of%20Zimbabwe%20-%20but%20opposition%20rejects%20result%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693104420000%2C%2