this%20venture%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20remarkable%20journey%20commercially%20since%202005%2C%20the%20couple%20reiterates%20that%20for%20them%20Woodway%20Estate%20has%20never%20been%20a%20structure%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20%E2%80%9Cliving%20thing%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20grown%20with%20them%20through%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWould%20we%20have%20done%20it%20any%20other%20way%3F%E2%80%9D%20Shreedev%20thinks%20aloud%20to%20himself%20for%20a%20moment.%20%E2%80%9CDefinitely%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692605280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWoodway-5114_11zon-1692368858-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Susmita%20and%20Shreedev's%20Woodway%20Estate%2C%20tucked%20in%20Chikmagalur%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20is%20a%20paradise%20for%20any%20nature%20lover.%20The%20freshly%20brewed%20coffee%20from%20the%20plantations%20is%20among%20the%20main%20attractions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A67%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327701%2Fcouple-restores-woodway-estate-british-era-home-into-heritage-homestay-in-chikmagalur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineer%20Uses%20Animated%20NCERT%20Syllabus%20To%20Turn%20Classrooms%20in%201000%20Govt%20Schools%20into%20Digital%20Hubs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Siya%20Umesh%20Jariya%20does%20not%20yawn%20in%20class%20anymore.%20For%20the%20Class%208%20student%20at%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Indore%2C%20learning%20is%20now%20fun%2C%20because%20she%20studies%20regular%20subjects%20through%20animated%20videos%20and%20cartoons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%