e%20a%20week.%20But%20the%20former%20has%20a%20direct%20impact%20on%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20Instagram%20%40foodpharmer%2C%20Revant%20educates%20about%20500%2C000%20of%20his%20followers%20on%20how%20they%20can%20make%20healthier%20choices.%20These%20include%20videos%20decoding%20labels%20of%20popular%20packaged%20noodles%2C%20drinks%2C%20biscuits%2C%20sauces%20and%20more%2C%20as%20well%20as%20helping%20people%20decide%20which%20bread%20is%20better%20for%20them%2C%20which%20drink%20they%20can%20choose%2C%20etc.%20He%20is%20also%20promoting%20small%20businesses%20that%20are%20%E2%80%9Crelatively%20healthier%E2%80%9D%20than%20the%20bigger%20brands.%20His%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20people%20choose%20better%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERemember%20this%20next%20time%20you%E2%80%99re%20at%20the%20supermarket%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwChJrSNO2I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwChJrSNO2I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopen